 display: inline-block;\\\">\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n            Clark and Sons specializes in Planned Maintenance Programs for Overhead Door, Dock, and Gate Equipment. Contact our team today to schedule your next PM inspection and ensure your equipment stays in top condition. Based on\\r\\n                    usage, we may recommend inspection frequencies such as Monthly, Quarterly, Semi-Annually, Annually, or Bi-Annually. Each inspection includes a detailed report on your door\\u2019s health and recommended replacement parts.\\r\\n                    Prefer to complete all work at once? No problem\\u2014we\\u2019re here to accommodate your schedule and make maintenance convenient for you\\r\\n          <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n      <\\/div>\\r\\n      <div class=\\\"row\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 text-center top-heading-sec\\\">\\r\\n          <h2>\\r\\n            Replacement Parts &amp; Service\\r\\n          <\\/h2>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n      <\\/div>\\r\\n      <div class=\\\"row commercial-emergency-service-sec\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-12 left-side\\\">\\r\\n          <h3>\\r\\n            Commercial Emergency Service\\r\\n          <\\/h3>\\r\\n          <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/front-assets\\/src\\/images\\/Commercial-Emergency-Service-image.webp\\\" class=\\\"img-fluid mobile-img resizable-image\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" width=\\\"777\\\" height=\\\"350\\\" style=\\\"position: relative; display: inline-block;\\\">\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n            At Clark and Sons, we\\u2019re here for you during any emergency\\u2014day or night, weekend or holiday, summer or winter. Our team works year-round to resolve your issues promptly and efficiently. Rely on our knowledgeable staff to\\r\\n                    deliver exceptional service when you need it most. Transform your expectations with Clark and Sons reliable emergency solutions.\\r\\n          <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-12 right-side\\\">\\r\\n          <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/front-assets\\/src\\/images\\/Commercial-Emergency-Service-image.webp\\\" class=\\\"img-fluid resizable-image\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" width=\\\"777\\\" height=\\\"350\\\" style=\\\"position: relative; display: inline-block;\\\">\\r\\n          <\\/div>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <!-- <div class=\\\"row makes-model-service-sec\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"col-xxl-9 col-xl-10 col-lg-10 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\\\">\\r\\n          <h2>\\r\\n            We service all makes and models of the following products:\\r\\n          <\\/h2>\\r\\n          <ul>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Sectional Overhead Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Rolling Steel Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Rolling Steel Security Grills\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Fire Rated and Security Counter Shutters\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Roll-Up Truck Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Traffic & Impact Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              PVC Strip Curtain Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Full View Overhead Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Rolling Steel Fire Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Mini Warehouse Sheet Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Door & Gate Operators\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              High-Speed Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n            <li>\\r\\n              Hollow Metal Doors\\r\\n            <\\/li>\\r\\n          <\\/ul>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n      <\\/div>\\r\\n      -->\\r\\n      <div class=\\\"row loading-dock-accessories-sec\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\\\">\\r\\n          <h2 class=\\\"models\\\">\\r\\n            We service all makes and models\\r\\n            <br>\\r\\n              of the following products:\\r\\n            <\\/h2>\\r\\n          <\\/div>\\r\\n          <div class=\\\"col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 list-left\\\">\\r\\n            <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Sectional Overhead Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Rolling Steel Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Rolling Steel Security Grills\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Fire Rated and Security Counter Shutters\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Roll-Up Truck Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Traffic &amp; Impact Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                PVC Strip Curtain Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n            <\\/ul>\\r\\n          <\\/div>\\r\\n          <div class=\\\"col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 list-right\\\">\\r\\n            <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Full View Overhead Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Rolling Steel Fire Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Mini Warehouse Sheet Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Door &amp; Gate Operators\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                High-Speed Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n              <li>\\r\\n                Hollow Metal Doors\\r\\n              <\\/li>\\r\\n            <\\/ul>\\r\\n          <\\/div>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n      <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/section>\"}', '{\"status\":1,\"section10_description\":\"\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-07-25 12:20:36', '2026-02-05 10:47:09', NULL);
INSERT INTO `home_page_settings` (`id`, `meta_title`, `meta_keyword`, `meta_description`, `banner_sec`, `system_setting_sec`, `service_heading_section`, `services_sec`, `garage_door`, `quote_sec`, `residential_sec`, `gallery_sec`, `areas_sec`, `faq_sec`, `why_choose_sec`, `blog_sec`, `calltoaction`, `design_sec`, `newgarage`, `testimonial`, `clientlogo`, `form_sec`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `deleted_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `deleted_at`) VALUES
(1, 'Delaware Garage Doors | Installation, Repair & Service | Clark and Sons', 'garage door delaware, garage door installation delaware, garage door company delaware', 'Clark & Sons is Delaware\'s trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, & maintenance. Call Now', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Delaware & Delmarva\'s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Delaware & the Entire Delmarva Peninsula for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"2862\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2794\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"2863\",\"banner_formtitle\":\"\",\"button_label\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Garage Door Experts in Delmarva Peninsula Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons specializes in the sales, installation, and servicing of top industry-leading garage door products throughout the entire Delmarva Peninsula. With four convenient locations, our skilled technicians provide dependable solutions, including expert spring repair, electrical troubleshooting, and complex installations.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family-owned and operated for three generations, we proudly bring over 60 years of unmatched expertise as Delaware\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. We help homeowners and contractors make informed decisions by offering exceptional value, personalized service, and a wide selection of quality products.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit our showroom today and explore your options, including visualizing your new garage door virtually!<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"503\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"service_head_title\":\"Our Comprehensive Garage Door Services\",\"service_head_description\":\"<p>At <b>Clark and Sons<\\/b>, our experienced team delivers professional, high-quality garage door solutions tailored specifically to your needs. With over 60 years serving Delaware and the Delmarva Peninsula, we guarantee reliable and efficient services that keep your garage doors safe, secure, and performing smoothly.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"services\":[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance your property\'s value and curb appeal with our premium residential and commercial garage doors. We offer a wide variety of styles, materials, and customization options, expertly installed by our skilled professionals to match your specific requirements.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Residential Garage Doors\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"service_img\":\"437\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Facing garage door troubles? Our skilled technicians offer prompt repairs and reliable parts replacement to quickly address any issues. From broken springs and snapped cables to damaged rollers, hinges, and weather seals\\u2014we handle it all. Our emergency repair services are available 24\\/7, ensuring minimal disruption to your daily routine.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Garage Door Repairs\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"service_img\":\"442\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>For seamless, secure garage access, our technicians specialize in installing, repairing, and servicing garage door openers. From traditional systems to advanced smart technology, we ensure your opener functions reliably and securely, providing maximum convenience and peace of mind.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Garage Door Openers\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"service_img\":\"440\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Regular maintenance and professional servicing significantly extend your garage door\\u2019s lifespan and reliability. Our comprehensive tune-ups include safety inspections, lubrication, balance adjustments, hardware tightening, and detailed performance checks to proactively prevent common problems and ensure seamless operation.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"service_img\":\"439\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Secure and strengthen your commercial or industrial property with our durable hollow metal entry door solutions. We offer expert installation, repair, and replacement of high-performance metal doors designed for enhanced security, fire protection, and longevity\\u2014ideal for warehouses, retail centers, and office buildings.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Hollow Metal Door\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"service_img\":\"443\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Streamline your business operations with our expert loading dock solutions. We install, maintain, and repair loading dock levelers, seals, shelters, and bumpers to ensure safe, efficient loading and unloading at your facility. Our team keeps your loading areas running smoothly and minimizes downtime.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"service_img\":\"444\"}]}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_button_name\":\"\",\"door_button_url\":\"\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"441\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"resi_title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance\",\"resi_sub_title\":\"Garage Door Service & Repair\",\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"resi_description\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"gallery_title\":\"Our Work\",\"gallery_sub_title\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Four Convenient Locations\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n<p>At Clark and Sons Garage Doors, we\'re committed to providing timely, reliable service across the entire Delmarva Peninsula. With four conveniently located offices, we\'re always nearby and ready to assist you with expert garage door installations, repairs, and maintenance.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div\\r\\nclass=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"two-column-list map-link\\\">\\r\\n    <li><b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/locations\\/newport-garage-doors\\/\\\"> Newport, Delaware<\\/a><\\/b> \\u2013 Proudly serving Wilmington, Newark, and surrounding communities. <\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/locations\\/salisbury-garage-doors\\/\\\">  Salisbury, Maryland<\\/a><\\/b> \\u2013 Conveniently located to serve the entire Eastern Shore area.<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/locations\\/dover-garage-doors\\/\\\"> Dover, Delaware<\\/a><\\/b> \\u2013 Centrally positioned to promptly assist homeowners and businesses throughout central Delaware.<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/locations\\/georgetown-garage-doors\\/\\\"> Georgetown, Delaware<\\/a><\\/b> \\u2013 Dedicated to providing dependable garage door solutions across southern Delaware and coastal communities.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"areas_button_name\":\"\",\"areas_button_url\":\"\",\"areas_img\":\"351\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"faq_title\":\"FAQ\'s\",\"faq_sub_title\":\"\",\"faq_img\":\"436\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"why_choose_title\":\"Why Choose Clark and Sons?\",\"why_choose_sub_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_img\":\"\",\"why_choose_img1\":\"433\",\"why_choose_img2\":\"432\",\"why_choose_img3\":\"431\",\"why_choose_img4\":\"435\",\"why_choose_img5\":\"430\",\"why_choose_img6\":\"434\",\"why_choose_title1\":\"Over 60 Years of Local Expertise\",\"why_choose_title2\":\"Fully Licensed & Insured Professionals\",\"why_choose_title3\":\"Family-Owned and Operated\",\"why_choose_title4\":\"Competitive & Transparent Pricing\",\"why_choose_title5\":\"Conveniently Located Across Delmarva\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"Top-Rated Customer Satisfaction\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"<p>Serving Delaware and the Delmarva Peninsula since 1963, we\'re Delaware\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. Our three-generation legacy ensures unmatched experience and reliable service.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"<p>Rest easy knowing your garage door is serviced by skilled, licensed, and fully insured technicians who prioritize quality, safety, and precision in every project.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"<p>As a family-owned business, we put trust, honesty, and personalized care into every job. Your satisfaction and safety are our top priorities.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"<p>We believe in fair pricing without hidden fees. Get clear, upfront quotes, affordable services, and exceptional value with every job.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>With four accessible locations, we\'re always nearby to quickly respond to your garage door installation, maintenance, or repair needs.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>We\\u2019ve earned the trust of thousands of homeowners and businesses through our commitment to quality work, fast response times, and friendly service, which is reflected in our 5-star reviews and loyal customer base.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"blog_title\":\"Recent Blogs\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"design_title\":\"Design Center\",\"button_name\":\"DESIGN NOW!\",\"button_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raynor.chameleonpower.com\\/?dealer=true&did=0027\",\"design_sub_title\":\"Customize your garage door!\",\"design_description\":\"<p>Build the garage door of your dreams with our design center. Quickly scroll through our wide range of models, styles, and options, and request a quote in a matter of minutes.<\\/p>\",\"design_img\":\"132\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"newgarage_title\":\"Need a New Garage Door?\",\"newgarage_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"testimonial_title\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"clientlogo_title\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"form_title\":\"Need a New Garage Door or Service?\",\"form_sub_title\":\"GET IN TOUCH!\",\"form_short_desc\":\"<p>For any inquiries about our company, products, or services, please do not hesitate to contact us.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '5', NULL, NULL, '2026-02-18 11:47:36', NULL),
(2, 'Delaware Garage Doors | Installation, Repair & Service | Clark and Sons', 'garage door delaware, garage door installation delaware, garage door company delaware', 'Clark & Sons is Delaware\'s trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, & maintenance. Call Now', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Delaware & Delmarva\'s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Delaware & the Entire Delmarva Peninsula for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"446\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2761\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"446\",\"banner_formtitle\":\"\",\"button_label\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Garage Door Experts in Delmarva Peninsula Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons specializes in the sales, installation, and servicing of top industry-leading garage door products throughout the entire Delmarva Peninsula. With four convenient locations, our skilled technicians provide dependable solutions, including expert spring repair, electrical troubleshooting, and complex installations.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family-owned and operated for three generations, we proudly bring over 60 years of unmatched expertise as Delaware\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. We help homeowners and contractors make informed decisions by offering exceptional value, personalized service, and a wide selection of quality products.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit our showroom today and explore your options, including visualizing your new garage door virtually!<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"503\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"service_head_title\":\"Our Comprehensive Garage Door Services\",\"service_head_description\":\"<p>At <b>Clark and Sons<\\/b>, our experienced team delivers professional, high-quality garage door solutions tailored specifically to your needs. With over 60 years serving Delaware and the Delmarva Peninsula, we guarantee reliable and efficient services that keep your garage doors safe, secure, and performing smoothly.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"services\":[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance your property\'s value and curb appeal with our premium residential and commercial garage doors. We offer a wide variety of styles, materials, and customization options, expertly installed by our skilled professionals to match your specific requirements.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Residential Garage Doors\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"service_img\":\"437\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Facing garage door troubles? Our skilled technicians offer prompt repairs and reliable parts replacement to quickly address any issues. From broken springs and snapped cables to damaged rollers, hinges, and weather seals\\u2014we handle it all. Our emergency repair services are available 24\\/7, ensuring minimal disruption to your daily routine.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Garage Door Repairs\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"service_img\":\"442\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>For seamless, secure garage access, our technicians specialize in installing, repairing, and servicing garage door openers. From traditional systems to advanced smart technology, we ensure your opener functions reliably and securely, providing maximum convenience and peace of mind.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Garage Door Openers\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"service_img\":\"440\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Regular maintenance and professional servicing significantly extend your garage door\\u2019s lifespan and reliability. Our comprehensive tune-ups include safety inspections, lubrication, balance adjustments, hardware tightening, and detailed performance checks to proactively prevent common problems and ensure seamless operation.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"service_img\":\"439\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Secure and strengthen your commercial or industrial property with our durable hollow metal entry door solutions. We offer expert installation, repair, and replacement of high-performance metal doors designed for enhanced security, fire protection, and longevity\\u2014ideal for warehouses, retail centers, and office buildings.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Hollow Metal Door\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"service_img\":\"443\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Streamline your business operations with our expert loading dock solutions. We install, maintain, and repair loading dock levelers, seals, shelters, and bumpers to ensure safe, efficient loading and unloading at your facility. Our team keeps your loading areas running smoothly and minimizes downtime.<\\/p>\",\"url_title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\",\"service_url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"service_img\":\"444\"}]}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_button_name\":\"\",\"door_button_url\":\"\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"441\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"(800) 479-3667\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"resi_title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance\",\"resi_sub_title\":\"Garage Door Service & Repair\",\"resi_button_name\":\"(800) 479-3667\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"resi_description\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"gallery_title\":\"Our Work\",\"gallery_sub_title\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Four Convenient Locations\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n<p>At Clark and Sons Garage Doors, we\'re committed to providing timely, reliable service across the entire Delmarva Peninsula. With four conveniently located offices, we\'re always nearby and ready to assist you with expert garage door installations, repairs, and maintenance.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div\\r\\nclass=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n<ul class=\\\"two-column-list map-link\\\">\\r\\n    <li><b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/locations\\/newport-garage-doors\\/\\\"> Newport, Delaware<\\/a><\\/b> \\u2013 Proudly serving Wilmington, Newark, and surrounding communities. <\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/locations\\/salisbury-garage-doors\\/\\\">  Salisbury, Maryland<\\/a><\\/b> \\u2013 Conveniently located to serve the entire Eastern Shore area.<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/locations\\/dover-garage-doors\\/\\\"> Dover, Delaware<\\/a><\\/b> \\u2013 Centrally positioned to promptly assist homeowners and businesses throughout central Delaware.<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><b><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/locations\\/georgetown-garage-doors\\/\\\"> Georgetown, Delaware<\\/a><\\/b> \\u2013 Dedicated to providing dependable garage door solutions across southern Delaware and coastal communities.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"areas_button_name\":\"\",\"areas_button_url\":\"\",\"areas_img\":\"351\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"faq_title\":\"FAQ\'s\",\"faq_sub_title\":\"\",\"faq_img\":\"436\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"why_choose_title\":\"Why Choose Clark and Sons?\",\"why_choose_sub_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_img\":\"\",\"why_choose_img1\":\"433\",\"why_choose_img2\":\"432\",\"why_choose_img3\":\"431\",\"why_choose_img4\":\"435\",\"why_choose_img5\":\"430\",\"why_choose_img6\":\"434\",\"why_choose_title1\":\"Over 60 Years of Local Expertise\",\"why_choose_title2\":\"Fully Licensed & Insured Professionals\",\"why_choose_title3\":\"Family-Owned and Operated\",\"why_choose_title4\":\"Competitive & Transparent Pricing\",\"why_choose_title5\":\"Conveniently Located Across Delmarva\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"Top-Rated Customer Satisfaction\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"<p>Serving Delaware and the Delmarva Peninsula since 1963, we\'re Delaware\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. Our three-generation legacy ensures unmatched experience and reliable service.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"<p>Rest easy knowing your garage door is serviced by skilled, licensed, and fully insured technicians who prioritize quality, safety, and precision in every project.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"<p>As a family-owned business, we put trust, honesty, and personalized care into every job. Your satisfaction and safety are our top priorities.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"<p>We believe in fair pricing without hidden fees. Get clear, upfront quotes, affordable services, and exceptional value with every job.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>With four accessible locations, we\'re always nearby to quickly respond to your garage door installation, maintenance, or repair needs.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>We\\u2019ve earned the trust of thousands of homeowners and businesses through our commitment to quality work, fast response times, and friendly service, which is reflected in our 5-star reviews and loyal customer base.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"blog_title\":\"Recent Blogs\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"(800) 479-3667\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"design_title\":\"Design Center\",\"button_name\":\"DESIGN NOW!\",\"button_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raynor.chameleonpower.com\\/?dealer=true&did=0027\",\"design_sub_title\":\"Customize your garage door!\",\"design_description\":\"<p>Build the garage door of your dreams with our design center. Quickly scroll through our wide range of models, styles, and options, and request a quote in a matter of minutes.<\\/p>\",\"design_img\":\"132\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"newgarage_title\":\"Need a New Garage Door?\",\"newgarage_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"testimonial_title\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"clientlogo_title\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"form_title\":\"Need a New Garage Door or Service?\",\"form_sub_title\":\"GET IN TOUCH!\",\"form_short_desc\":\"<p>For any inquiries about our company, products, or services, please do not hesitate to contact us.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '5', NULL, NULL, '2026-01-26 06:32:18', NULL);
INSERT INTO `loadingdockdoors` (`id`, `meta_title`, `meta_keyword`, `meta_description`, `title`, `subtitle`, `description`, `bannerimage`, `c_s_button_name`, `c_s_button_url`, `section2`, `section3`, `section4`, `section5`, `section6`, `section7`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `deleted_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `deleted_at`) VALUES
(1, 'Full-Service Loading Dock Solutions in Delaware', 'loading dock equipment installers delaware', 'Clark & Sons delivers full-service loading dock solutions in Delaware — from equipment sales and expert installation to 24/7 emergency repair and support. Call today.', 'Loading Dock Equipment Experts Delaware', NULL, '<p>We specialize in mechanical, hydraulic, and vertical storing dock levelers—as well as dock shelters &amp; seals, dock bumpers, dock lights, and a full range of replacement parts &amp; accessories. We service all makes and models with precision and care. </p>', '2573', 'GET A QUOTE', '#getafreequote', '{\"status\":1,\"section2_title\":\"What Dock Equipment will work with your application?\",\"section2_description\":\"<p>\\r\\n                    Welcome to Clark and Sons, where excellence meets innovation in loading dock solutions. For years, we\'ve been dedicated to providing top-quality products paired with trusted, leading-edge technology designed to elevate your dock operations. Our commitment goes beyond supplying equipment\\u2014we partner with you to ensure every facet of your loading dock experience is seamless. Whether you\'re seeking advanced safety features, reliable performance, or efficient design, our solutions are tailored to fit your unique needs.<br><br>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tServing the greater Delaware area, we take pride in offering comprehensive services that include expert consultation, professional installation, and ongoing support. <br><br>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tAt Clark and Sons, we understand that the right dock equipment is vital for maintaining smooth operations and enhancing workplace safety. Let us help you complete your loading dock requirements with precision and care\\u2014because your success is our mission.\\r\\n                <\\/p>\",\"section2_image\":\"\",\"sec2_title_1\":\"Hydraulic Dock Levelers\",\"sec2_description_1\":\"<p>Transform your dock operations with our hydraulic dock levelers. Engineered for superior safety and efficiency, they ensure smooth transitions between truck and dock, reducing manual labor and boosting productivity. Ideal for warehouses, distribution centers, and shipping facilities, these robust solutions handle heavy use while streamlining workflow. Invest in our hydraulic dock levelers to minimize downtime, enhance safety, and maximize operational performance.<\\/p>\",\"sec2_image_1\":\"2574\",\"sec2_title_2\":\"Mechanical Dock Levelers\",\"sec2_description_2\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\t\\t                Experience unmatched efficiency with our Mechanical Dock Levelers. Designed for durability and ease of use, these levelers ensure smooth transitions for loading and unloading across various vehicles, enhancing safety and reducing downtime. Ideal for busy warehouses and distribution centers, our solutions streamline operations while protecting both personnel and equipment. Elevate your dock\'s performance with a proven technology trusted for its reliability and versatility in handling diverse loading environments.\\r\\n\\t\\t            <\\/p>\",\"sec2_image_2\":\"2575\",\"sec2_title_3\":\"Vertical Storing Dock or Edge of Dock Levelers\",\"sec2_description_3\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\t\\t                Experience enhanced efficiency and safety with our Vertical Storing Dock and Edge-of-Dock Levelers. Designed for compact spaces, these levelers streamline loading and unloading operations, reducing floor clutter while maximizing vertical storage. Ideal for busy warehouses, manufacturing facilities, and distribution centers, they provide smooth transitions for trucks, improve ergonomics, and accelerate turnaround times. Trust our innovative solutions to boost productivity, safeguard your team, and optimize your dock operations.\\r\\n\\t\\t            <\\/p>\",\"sec2_image_3\":\"2579\",\"sec2_title_4\":\"Scissor Lift & Multiple Stage Lift Tables\",\"sec2_image_4\":\"2577\",\"sec2_description_4\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\t\\t                Elevate your operations with our versatile Scissor Lifts and Multiple Stage Lift Tables. Engineered to enhance efficiency and safety, these lifts offer seamless height adjustments for ergonomic loading, precise assembly, and secure storage across various industries\\u2014from warehousing to manufacturing. Reduce labor costs, minimize injury risks, and streamline your workflow with robust, intuitive technology designed to meet your most demanding requirements. Experience the perfect synergy of functionality and innovation today.\\r\\n\\t\\t            <\\/p>\"}', '{\"status\":1,\"section3_title\":\"Loading Dock Accessories\",\"section3_description\":\"\",\"section3_image\":\"\",\"sec3_title_1\":\"Traffic & Guide Lights\",\"sec3_description_1\":\"<p>Ensure safety and visibility at your loading dock with our durable traffic and guide lights, designed to improve workflow, direct vehicles efficiently, and prevent accidents during loading operations.<\\/p>\",\"sec3_image_1\":\"2581\",\"sec3_title_2\":\"Dock Lights\",\"sec3_description_2\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\t\\t                Illuminate your loading dock with high-quality, energy-efficient dock lights, offering superior brightness and long-lasting durability to improve visibility and safety during night-time or low-light operations.\\r\\n\\t\\t            <\\/p>\",\"sec3_image_2\":\"2582\",\"sec3_title_3\":\"Wheel Chocks\",\"sec3_description_3\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\t\\t                Prevent accidents and enhance safety with our sturdy wheel chocks, designed to secure vehicles in place during loading and unloading, ensuring stability and reducing the risk of movement.\\r\\n\\t\\t            <\\/p>\",\"sec3_image_3\":\"2579\",\"sec3_title_4\":\"Dock Bumpers\",\"sec3_image_4\":\"2580\",\"sec3_description_4\":\"<p>\\r\\n\\t\\t                Protect your loading dock and vehicles with heavy-duty dock bumpers, designed to absorb impact, reduce wear, and provide long-lasting protection against accidental collisions in busy dock environments.\\r\\n\\t\\t            <\\/p>\"}', '{\"status\":1,\"section4_title\":\"We Service All Loading Dock Equipment\",\"section4_sub_title\":\"Parts, Service and Repair for <br> Loading Dock Equipment\",\"section4_description\":\"<p>\\r\\n                    When an emergency strikes, we\'re here to assist. Day or night, weekend or holiday, summer or winter, we operate year-round to resolve your issues quickly and efficiently. Exceed your expectations with the expert team at Anchor Doors &amp; Service Inc.\\r\\n                <\\/p>\",\"section4_image\":\"2578\"}', '{\"status\":1,\"section5_title\":\"Loading Dock Accessories\",\"section5_description\":\"<div class=\\\"col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 list-left\\\">\\r\\n        \\t  \\t<ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Mechanical Dock Levelers<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Hydraulic Dock Levelers<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Vertical Storing Dock Levelers<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Stationary Truck Shelters<\\/li>\\t\\t    \\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Stationary Inflatable Truck Shelters<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n        \\t  <\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 list-right\\\">\\r\\n        \\t  \\t<ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\t\\t\\t\\t   \\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Retractable Dock Shelters<\\/li>\\t\\t\\t\\t    \\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Rain Shroud Dock Shelter Seal<\\/li>\\t\\t\\t\\t    \\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Fixed Header Dock Seal<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Adjustable Head Curtain Dock Seal<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t    <li>Loading Dock Accessories<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n        \\t  <\\/div>\",\"section5_image\":\"\"}', '{\"status\":1,\"section6_title1\":\"\",\"section6_description1\":\"\",\"section6_image1\":\"\",\"section6_title2\":\"\",\"section6_description2\":\"\",\"section6_image2\":\"\"}', '{\"status\":1,\"section7_description\":\"\",\"section7_image\":\"\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-07-25 06:02:49', '2025-12-29 10:45:40', NULL);
INSERT INTO `location_settings` (`id`, `location`, `slug`, `status`, `type`, `banner_sec`, `system_setting_sec`, `services_sec`, `service_heading_section`, `garage_door`, `quote_sec`, `residential_sec`, `gallery_sec`, `areas_sec`, `faq_sec`, `why_choose_sec`, `blog_sec`, `calltoaction`, `design_sec`, `newgarage`, `testimonial`, `clientlogo`, `form_sec`, `meta_tags_sec`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `deleted_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `deleted_at`) VALUES
(1, 'newport', 'newport-garage-doors', 1, 'location', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Newport\'s Most Trusted Garage <br>Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Newport Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"368\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"454\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2796\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Newport\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons is a premier garage door company in Newport, specializing in the sales, installation, and service of industry-leading residential and commercial garage doors. From durable overhead doors to advanced openers and custom finishes, we deliver top-quality solutions that enhance security, functionality, and curb appeal.<\\/p><p>With over 60 years of experience and a dedicated team based right here in Newport, we offer dependable services including expert spring replacement, electrical troubleshooting, hardware upgrades, and complex installations. Our technicians are trained to handle every job with precision, care, and a commitment to long-lasting performance.<\\/p><p>Visit our conveniently located Newport showroom to explore your options \\u2014 and use our virtual visualization tools to see how your new garage door will look before installation.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"499\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Boost your property\\u2019s curb appeal and functionality with our high-quality residential and commercial garage doors. Choose from a wide selection of styles, materials, and custom features - all professionally installed to suit your specific needs and architectural preferences. Our skilled technicians ensure every installation is precise, durable, and built to elevate both the look and value of your home or business.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"455\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Dealing with a malfunctioning garage door? We offer same-day garage door repair services across Newport for broken springs, off-track doors, snapped cables, misaligned sensors, and more. We are available 24\\/7 for emergencies - because we know your time matters.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"450\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>\\r\\nEnsure smooth, secure access to your garage with expert opener services. Our technicians specialize in the installation, repair, and maintenance of all types of garage door openers - from reliable traditional models to the latest innovative technology systems. We make sure your opener operates quietly, efficiently, and safely, giving you maximum convenience and long-term peace of mind.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"448\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>\\r\\nKeep your garage door operating at its best with routine maintenance and service. Regular servicing extends your system\'s life and improves its safety, efficiency, and reliability. Our comprehensive tune-ups include thorough safety inspections, precision balance adjustments, lubrication of moving parts, hardware tightening, and complete performance checks\\u2014all designed to prevent costly breakdowns and ensure smooth, worry-free operation year-round.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"457\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>\\r\\nProtect your commercial or industrial space with our heavy-duty hollow metal entry doors. Engineered for superior strength, security, and fire resistance, our high-performance metal doors are ideal for warehouses, retail facilities, and office buildings. We provide expert installation, repair, and replacement services, ensuring long-lasting durability and code-compliant protection tailored to your property\\u2019s specific needs.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"451\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Optimize your facility\\u2019s efficiency with professional loading dock solutions. We specialize in the installation, maintenance, and repair of dock levelers, seals, shelters, and bumpers\\u2014ensuring safe, streamlined loading and unloading processes. Our skilled technicians help reduce downtime, improve workplace safety, and maintain your dock operations at peak performance.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"452\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive <br> Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has been delivering trusted garage door services in Newport for over 60 years, offering expert installation, fast repairs, and reliable maintenance with a personal touch. As a locally established name in the garage door industry, our experienced team is dedicated to keeping your garage door safe, secure, and operating smoothly year-round. Whether you\'re dealing with a broken spring, planning a new installation, or need a seasonal tune-up, we provide dependable solutions built to last.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"449\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\n    Clark and Sons delivers fast, dependable service across a vast network of cities and towns in New Castle County, DE and\\r\\n    <br>\\r\\n      Chester County, PA, Whether you\'re a homeowner or business owner, we\'re right around the comer and ready to help.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n  <\\/div>\\r\\n  <div class=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n    <ul class=\\\"two-column-list area-sec-column-list\\\">\\r\\n      <li>\\r\\n        <b>\\r\\n        New Castle County, Delaware\\r\\n      <\\/b>\\r\\n      <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n        <li>\\r\\n          Bear\\r\\n        <\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>\\r\\n         <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-areas\\/claymont-de-garage-doors\\/\\\">\\r\\n          Claymont\\r\\n        <\\/a>\\r\\n        <\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>\\r\\n          Delaware City\\r\\n