without hidden fees. Get clear, upfront quotes, affordable services, and exceptional value with every job.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>With four accessible locations, we\'re always nearby to quickly respond to your garage door installation, maintenance, or repair needs.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>We\\u2019ve earned the trust of thousands of homeowners and businesses through our commitment to quality work, fast response times, and friendly service, which is reflected in our 5-star reviews and loyal customer base.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A  QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"meta_title\":\"Newport Garage Doors | Installation, Repair & Service Near Me\",\"meta_keyword\":\"garage door installation newport, garage door repair newport, garage door service newport\",\"meta_description\":\"Clark & Sons is Newport\';s trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, &  maintenance. Call Now\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-05-21 13:21:13', '2026-02-12 11:44:34', NULL),
(2, 'dover', 'dover-garage-doors', 1, 'location', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Dover\'s Most Trusted Garage <br> Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Dover Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"466\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"466\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2797\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Dover\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons is the premier garage door company in Dover, specializing in selling, installing, and servicing top-tier residential and commercial garage doors. We deliver secure, stylish, and high-performing garage door solutions from heavy-duty overhead doors to quiet openers and elegant finishes.<\\/p><p>With over 60 years of trusted experience and a dedicated local team in Dover, we handle every job with precision\\u2014offering services like spring replacement, sensor alignment, hardware upgrades, and even the most complex installations. Our technicians are trained to deliver results that last, all while prioritizing your safety and satisfaction.<\\/p><p>Visit our conveniently located Dover showroom to explore a wide range of products\\u2014and \\r\\nuse our innovative visualization tools to preview your door before installation.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"500\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Improve your property\\u2019s curb appeal and efficiency with our expert installation of\\r\\n                                    residential and commercial garage doors. Choose from an extensive range of\\r\\n                                    materials, colors, and custom features. Our technicians ensure precise fits,\\r\\n                                    long-term durability, and eye-catching design tailored to your Dover property.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"468\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Experiencing garage door issues? Our same-day repair service in Dover is available\\r\\n                                    for broken springs, misaligned doors, snapped cables, malfunctioning remotes, and\\r\\n                                    more. We\'re here for emergency situations - because your time and safety are our\\r\\n                                    priorities.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"462\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Trust us for the installation and repair of all garage door opener types, from\\r\\n                                    traditional chain drives to innovative, quiet systems. We ensure that your garage\\r\\n                                    opens efficiently, operates silently, and keeps your home or business secure every\\r\\n                                    time you press that button.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"460\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Ensure your garage door performs at its best year-round with routine maintenance.\\r\\n                                    Regular service not only extends the lifespan of your system but also enhances\\r\\n                                    safety, efficiency, and overall reliability. Our detailed maintenance includes a\\r\\n                                    full safety inspection, precise balance adjustments, lubrication of key components,\\r\\n                                    tightening of hardware, and complete system testing. These proactive tune-ups help\\r\\n                                    prevent unexpected breakdowns, reduce long-term repair costs, and keep your garage\\r\\n                                    door running smoothly with confidence and peace of mind.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"459\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Secure your commercial space with our rugged hollow metal doors. Designed for\\r\\n                                    strength, fire resistance, and security, these are perfect for retail buildings,\\r\\n                                    offices, and warehouses. We install and service entry systems that meet building\\r\\n                                    codes and protect what matters most.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"463\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Maximize your facility\\u2019s productivity with expert loading dock solutions tailored to\\r\\n                                    your operational needs. We provide professional installation, maintenance, and\\r\\n                                    repair of dock levelers, seals, shelters, and bumpers\\u2014ensuring every loading and\\r\\n                                    unloading process is safe, efficient, and compliant. Our experienced technicians\\r\\n                                    work quickly to minimize downtime, enhance on-site safety, and keep your dock\\r\\n                                    equipment running at peak performance for smooth, uninterrupted operations.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"464\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive <br>Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has been Dover\\u2019s go-to name in garage doors for over 60 years. We offer reliable\\r\\n                    installations, fast repairs, and preventative maintenance designed to keep your garage door system\\r\\n                    running safely and smoothly year-round. Whether you\'re tackling a broken cable or considering a\\r\\n                    complete upgrade, our skilled team is here to deliver lasting results you can count on.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"461\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\n    Clark and Sons proudly delivers fast, dependable garage door services throughout Kent County, DE, and surrounding\\r\\n    <br>\\r\\n      counties in Maryland. We\'re just a call away w