(3, 'georgetown', 'georgetown-garage-doors', 1, 'location', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Georgetown\'s Most Trusted Garage  Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Georgetown Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"484\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"485\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2798\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Georgetown\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons is a leading garage door company in Georgetown. We specialize in the sales, installation, and service of industry-leading residential and commercial garage doors. From long-lasting overhead doors to quiet openers and modern finishes, we deliver expert solutions that enhance safety, performance, and curb appeal.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>With over 60 years of hands-on experience and a trusted team based right here in Georgetown, we deliver reliable garage door services you can count on. From spring replacements and electrical troubleshooting to hardware upgrades and complex installations, our skilled technicians complete every job with precision, care, and a focus on long-term performance and safety.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit our conveniently located Georgetown showroom to browse our extensive product lineup\\u2014and use our virtual visualization tools to preview how your new garage door will look on your home.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"501\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance your property\\u2019s curb appeal and performance with top-quality residential and\\r\\n                                    commercial garage doors. We offer a broad range of styles, materials, and\\r\\n                                    customizable features\\u2014expertly installed to match your unique needs and complement\\r\\n                                    your home or business architecture. Every installation is handled with precision and\\r\\n                                    care, ensuring long-lasting durability and a polished look that adds real value to\\r\\n                                    your property.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"483\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Is your garage door acting up? We offer fast, same-day repair service across\\r\\n                                    Georgetown for common issues like broken springs, misaligned sensors, snapped\\r\\n                                    cables, or noisy openers. We\\u2019re available 24\\/7 for emergency calls\\u2014because your\\r\\n                                    safety and time matter.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"477\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Enjoy smooth, secure access to your garage with our professional opener services. Our\\r\\n                                    experienced technicians install, repair, and maintain all garage door opener\\r\\n                                    types\\u2014from dependable traditional units to advanced intelligent systems. We ensure\\r\\n                                    your opener runs quietly, efficiently, and safely, delivering everyday convenience\\r\\n                                    and reliable performance you can trust.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"475\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Protect your garage door investment with regular maintenance. Our regular tune-ups\\r\\n                                    include complete safety inspections, balance adjustments, hardware checks, and\\r\\n                                    lubrication of all moving parts. Prevent costly breakdowns and keep your system\\r\\n                                    running worry-free year-round with our garage door maintenance plans.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"474\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Secure your commercial property with heavy-duty hollow metal doors. Built for\\r\\n                                    durability, fire resistance, and security, these doors are ideal for offices,\\r\\n                                    warehouses, and retail buildings. We install and service metal doors that are\\r\\n                                    tailored to your layout, meet building codes, and provide lasting protection.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"478\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Improve your facility\\u2019s safety and productivity with our professional loading dock\\r\\n                                    solutions. We install, repair, and maintain dock levelers, bumpers, seals, and\\r\\n                                    shelters\\u2014ensuring smooth, compliant operations. Our local technicians work\\r\\n                                    efficiently to minimize downtime and optimize your workflow.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"479\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive <br>Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has proudly delivered reliable garage door services in Georgetown for over 60 yea