(4, 'salisbary', 'salisbury-garage-doors', 1, 'location', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Salisbury\'s Most Trusted  Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Salisbury Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"495\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"493\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2799\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Salisbury\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons is the trusted garage door company serving Salisbury and the surrounding region. We specialize in top-tier residential and commercial garage door solutions, from high-strength overhead doors to smart openers and custom finishes. We deliver durable, secure, and attractive products that add real value to your property.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>With over 60 years of hands-on experience and a dedicated local team in Salisbury, we provide expert services including spring repairs, opener diagnostics, hardware upgrades, and full-system installations. Every job is handled with skill, care, and a commitment to delivering lasting, high-quality results.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Stop by our conveniently located Salisbury showroom to explore our wide range of options and use our virtual tools to visualize how your new garage door will look before we install it.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"502\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Upgrade your home or business with expertly installed garage doors that enhance curb\\r\\n                                    appeal and functionality. Choose from various durable materials, styles, and custom\\r\\n                                    features tailored to your building\\u2019s archi