(6, 'berlin', 'berlin-md-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Berlin\'s Most Trusted  Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Berlin Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"514\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"511\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2795\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Berlin\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has proudly served the Berlin community for over six decades with expert garage door services that deliver performance, safety, and long-term value. Specializing in residential and commercial garage door sales, installation, and repair, we offer a wide range of solutions to meet the needs of Berlin homes and businesses. Whether you\\u2019re replacing a worn-out opener or installing a new custom garage door, we\\u2019ve got you covered.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our experienced technicians understand the unique needs of Berlin property owners and take pride in offering professional, prompt, and personalized service. Every job is completed with unmatched precision and care, from broken springs and track issues to smart opener upgrades and full replacements.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit our showroom near Berlin to explore various garage doors, openers, and finishes. Use our virtual design tool to preview your new door before installation and feel confident in your choice.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"504\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance your Berlin property with a beautiful, professionally installed garage door.\\r\\n                                    Choose from various designs, colors, and finishes\\u2014c