(10, 'lewes', 'lewes-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Lewes Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Lewes Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"526\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"524\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2800\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Lewes Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has proudly served the Lewes community with expert garage door solutions tailored to the needs of local homeowners and businesses. We specialize in the sales, installation, and repair of residential and commercial garage doors\\u2014offering high-performance options that boost curb appeal, security, and everyday convenience. From classic overhead doors to advanced openers with smart technology, we deliver reliable upgrades that enhance your property.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our skilled Lewes-based team handles everything from broken spring repairs and opener replacements to complete garage door installations and routine maintenance. Every service is performed with precision, care, and a commitment to long-lasting results\\u2014backed by decades of hands-on experience.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Stop by our showroom near Lewes to browse our extensive collection of garage doors and accessories. Use our virtual design tool to preview your new door\'s appearance before installation\\u2014making your decision easy and stress-free.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"516\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Improve your property\'s look and function with expertly installed garage doors. We offer a wide range of styles, finishes, and features for both residential and commercial properties\\u2014carefully installed to fit your structure, enhance curb appeal, and provide lasting value.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"527\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>If your garage door is stuck, noisy, or off-track, our Lewes technicians are ready to help. We offer fast, same-day service for spring replacements, cable issues, roller damage, and opener malfunctions. Plus, our 24\\/7 emergency repairs ensure you\\u2019re never left without support.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"521\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Upgrade to smooth, quiet, and reliable access with our garage door opener solutions. Whether you prefer traditional or smart-controlled systems, we install and service all major brands to ensure safe, seamless operation tailored to your daily needs.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"519\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Routine maintenance is the key to avoiding breakdowns and extending your garage door\\u2019s lifespan. Our comprehensive tune-ups include spring tension checks, track adjustments, safety tests, and full-system lubrication\\u2014keeping your door running like new.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"518\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Secure your commercial property with heavy-duty hollow metal doors, ideal for retail buildings, offices, and industrial sites. We install and service code-compliant entry doors designed for durability, fire safety, and security\\u2014built t