(8, 'dewey-beach', 'dewey-beach-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Dewey Beach\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Dewey Beach Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"537\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"535\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2801\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Dewey Beach\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has been the trusted name as a garage door company in Dewey Beach. We specialize in the sales, service, and installation of top-tier residential and commercial garage doors. Whether you\'re upgrading a coastal home or need dependable doors for a business property, our team delivers safe, stylish, and long-lasting results.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Locally based and family-owned, our team understands the unique needs of Dewey Beach homeowners and businesses. From repairing noisy openers and broken springs to installing modern garage doors with smart controls, we bring precision, care, and decades of expertise to every project.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit our nearby showroom to explore our complete line of garage doors and accessories\\u2014and visualize your perfect setup with our virtual visualization tools before installation.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"528\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>With our expertly installed garage doors, you can add value, security, and curb appeal to your property. Choose from various materials, colors, finishes, and hardware options to match your design preferences. Every installation is handled carefully by trained technicians who prioritize safety, du