g\":\"533\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Improve workplace efficiency with professionally installed and serviced loading dock equipment. From bumpers and seals to levelers and shelters, we provide safe, durable, and OSHA-compliant solutions tailored to your facility\\u2019s needs. Our local technicians work fast to reduce downtime and keep your operations running.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"534\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive <br> Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons proudly offers expert garage door services in Dewey Beach for over 60 years. Whether you need a brand-new installation, emergency repair, or ongoing maintenance, we\\u2019re here with fast, friendly, and reliable service you can count on. We tailor every solution to fit your needs, budget, and style\\u2014because your home deserves nothing less.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"531\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Re