(9, 'fenwick-island', 'fenwick-island-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Fenwick Island\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Fenwick Island Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"560\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"558\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2803\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Fenwick Island\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has been Fenwick Island\\u2019s trusted name for garage door services prioritizing safety, style, and long-term performance. We specialize in the sales, installation, and service of premium residential and commercial garage doors\\u2014perfect for the unique demands of coastal living. Whether you need a weather-resistant overhead door or a quiet, smart opener system, we deliver dependable results built to last.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our local Fenwick Island team understands what matters most to area homeowners and businesses. From broken springs and damaged tracks to complex installations and energy-efficient upgrades, we handle every job with care, precision, and unmatched craftsmanship.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit our nearby showroom to explore various garage door styles and accessories. With our virtual visualization tool, you can preview how different doors will look on your property before making a final decision.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"563\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Upgrade your home or business with a durable, professionally installed garage door. Choose from various styles, materials, and finishes\\u2014customized to suit your aesthetic and funct