(14, 'servicearea', NULL, 1, 'location', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Delaware\'s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving the Entire Delmarva Peninsula for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"368\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"340\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Garage Door Experts in Delmarva Peninsula Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons specializes in the sales, installation, and servicing of top industry-leading garage door products throughout the entire Delmarva Peninsula. With four convenient locations, our skilled technicians provide dependable solutions, including expert spring repair, electrical troubleshooting, and complex installations.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family-owned and operated for three generations, we proudly bring over 60 years of unmatched expertise as Delaware\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. We help homeowners and contractors make informed decisions by offering exceptional value, personalized service, and a wide selection of quality products.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit our showroom today and explore your options, including visualizing your new garage door virtually!<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"362\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Facing garage door troubles? Our skilled technicians offer prompt repairs and reliable parts replacement to quickly address any issues. From broken springs and snapped cables to damaged rollers, hinges, and weather seals\\u2014we handle it all. Our emergency repair services are available 24\\/7, ensuring minimal disruption to your daily routine.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"356\",\"url\":null,\"urltitle\":null},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Regular maintenance and professional servicing significantly extend your garage door\\u2019s lifespan and reliability. Our comprehensive tune-ups include safety inspections, lubrication, balance adjustments, hardware tightening, and detailed performance checks to proactively prevent common problems and ensure seamless operation.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"352\",\"url\":null,\"urltitle\":null}]', '{\"title\":\"\",\"description\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":0,\"door_title\":\"\",\"door_sub_title\":\"\",\"garage_door_description\":\"\",\"garage_img\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":0,\"quote_title\":\"\",\"quotesub_title\":\"\",\"quote_button_name\":\"\",\"quote_button_url\":\"\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"\",\"resi_button_url\":\"\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n    <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\n       At Clark and Sons Garage Doors, we\'re committed to providing timely, reliable service across the entire Maryland and Delaware. With four conveniently located offices, we\'re always nearby and ready to assist you with expert garage door installations, repairs, and maintenance.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"parent-location\\\">\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"proud-area-we-serve-location section-one\\\">\\r\\n        <h2 class=\\\"location-title\\\">Delaware <\\/h2>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"line-area\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"delaware-section\\\">\\r\\n            \\r\\n            <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n                <li><h5>New Castle County<\\/h5>\\r\\n                    <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n                        <li>Bear<\\/li>\\r\\n                        <li>Claymont<\\/li>\\r\\n                        <li>Delaware City<\\/li>\\r\\n  