ecretary<\\/li>\\r\\n                    <li>Taylors Island<\\/li>\\r\\n                    <li>Toddville<\\/li>\\r\\n                    <li>Vienna<\\/li>\\r\\n                    <li>Wingate<\\/li>\\r\\n                    <li>Woolford<\\/li>\\r\\n                    \\r\\n\\r\\n                    <\\/ul>\\r\\n                <\\/li>\\r\\n            <\\/ul>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"areas_button_name\":\"\",\"areas_button_url\":\"\",\"areas_img\":\"371\"}', '{\"checked\":0,\"faq_title\":\"\",\"faq_sub_title\":\"\",\"faq_img\":\"\"}', '{\"checked\":0,\"why_choose_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_sub_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_img1\":\"\",\"why_choose_img2\":\"\",\"why_choose_img3\":\"\",\"why_choose_img4\":\"\",\"why_choose_img5\":\"\",\"why_choose_img6\":\"\",\"why_choose_title1\":\"\",\"why_choose_title2\":\"\",\"why_choose_title3\":\"\",\"why_choose_title4\":\"\",\"why_choose_title5\":\"\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":0,\"calltoaction_title\":\"\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"\",\"button_url\":\"\",\"call_button_name\":\"\",\"call_button_url\":\"\",\"call_button_desc\":\"\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":0,\"meta_title\":\"\",\"meta_keyword\":\"\",\"meta_description\":\"\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-05-21 13:21:13', '2025-12-08 23:58:12', '2025-12-13 09:49:19'),
(15, 'middle-town', 'middletown-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Middletown\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly serving Middletown communities for the last 60 years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"606\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"604\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2804\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Your Local Garage Door Experts in Middletown, DE, Serving Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>For over six decades, Clark & Sons Garage Doors has been the trusted name for garage door installation, repair, and maintenance across Middletown. They\\u2019re serving homeowners and businesses. We are a team of experts who bring trusted expertise and exceptional service to every job, along with reliable products. We want to continue our legacy with the Middletown, DE team, and that\\u2019s why we are here to provide you with comprehensive garage door installation solutions. You can get anything from stylish new installations to fast, dependable repairs. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>There could be any issues in your home, anything from a broken spring to a noisy operation, or an outdated door. We got it covered for you. We have a team of professional workmanship, and we will provide you with the best services, offering honest pricing and long-lasting results. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>You can search for us in your nearby location and explore our interactive design tools to virtually preview your garage door before making a decision. Don\\u2019t wait, get started today and see your new garage door come to life!<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"608\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>You can give your property a makeover with a brand new garage door design. If you are someone who wants something stylish but durable, consider it done with us. We offer a wide range of residential to commercial garage doors, you can get them in steel, wood, aluminum, etc. <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"607\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repair Services\",\"description\":\"<p>You don\'t want to risk your safety with that malfunctioning garage door, right? That is why you should let our experts assist you today. Our professionals offer fast and same-day repairs throughout Middletown. You can get services for everything from broken springs to snapped-off track doors, and more. <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"601\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Installation & Repair\",\"description\":\"<p>You want hands-on installation and repairs? We\'ve got you covered. You can get the latest teaching from all leading brands, with Wi-Fi-enabled services. Your safety is our priority. If your opener is making unusual noises and not responding correctly, contact us today, and we will fix it for you promptly.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"611\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Preventive Maintenance & Safety Checks\",\"description\":\"<p>\\r\\nJust like your body needs regular maintenance with food and other essentials, your garage door also requires regular maintenance. The goal is to save you from costly breakdowns by extending your garage door\\u2019s lifespan. We offer complete maintenance that includes balance testing to adjustments. We will inspect all the wear and tear and make the necessary repairs.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"609\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Protect your business with our fire-rated hollow metal doors, built for durability, safety, and full code compliance. These low-maintenance entrance systems offer long-lasting security, making them ideal for commercial buildings, schools, and warehouses in Middletown.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"602\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>\\r\\nKeep your facility running efficiently and safely with our professional loading dock equipment services. From installation to maintenance, we handle dock levelers, seals, bumpers, and more, ensuring your operations run smoothly and comply with safety standards.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"603\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Complete Garage Door Solutions for <br> Middletown Homes & Businesses\",\"description\":\"<p>With Clark &amp; Sons, you will get services that will deliver more than just good service; but you will get reliable and long-lasting garage door solutions. Whether it\'s your home or business space, we handle everything throughout Middletown, Delaware. You can get anything from modern installations to quick repairs.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"600\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\n Clark & Sons proudly offers expert garage door installation, repair, and maintenance services in Middletown, DE and the surrounding areas. <br>Our local professionals are only a phone call away if you require immediate, qualified assistance.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n <li><b>Middletown, Delaware<\\/b>\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n<li>Appoquinimink<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Bunker Hill<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Christiana Estates<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>North Middletown<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>South Middletown<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>St. Anne\\u2019s<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li>Summit Bridge Area<\\/li>\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n <\\/li>\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"bottom-content text-center\\\">For courteous, dependable, and timely garage door service in the Odessa area, call us today at <a href=\\\"tel:+18004793667\\\">(800) 479-3667.<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"areas_button_name\":\"\",\"areas_button_url\":\"\",\"areas_img\":\"359\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"faq_title\":\"FAQ\'s\",\"faq_sub_title\":\"\",\"faq_img\":\"610\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"why_choose_title\":\"Why Choose Clark and Sons?\",\"why_choose_sub_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_img1\":\"433\",\"why_choose_img2\":\"432\",\"why_choose_img3\":\"431\",\"why_choose_img4\":\"435\",\"why_choose_img5\":\"430\",\"why_choose_img6\":\"434\",\"why_choose_title1\":\"Decades of Trusted Experience\",\"why_choose_title2\":\"Comprehensive Service Range\",\"why_choose_title3\":\"High-Quality Materials & Brands\",\"why_choose_title4\":\"Fast Response & Emergency Assistance\",\"why_choose_title5\":\"Transparent Pricing, No Hidden Fees\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"100% Customer Satisfaction Guarantee\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"<p>With over 60 years in the garage door industry, our team brings unmatched expertise to every project, ensuring precise installation, timely repairs, and reliable service that stands the test of time.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"<p>From residential garage door installations to commercial loading dock systems, our trained professionals handle all your needs under one roof with care and efficiency.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"<p>We partner with trusted manufacturers to deliver high-quality doors and openers that last. Every product we install is durable, weather-resistant, and designed for performance.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"<p>Garage door stuck or opener malfunctioning? Our quick-response team ensures you get same-day service and peace of mind when you need it most.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>We maintain transparency with your customers. With Clark &amp; Sons, you will never find any hidden charges. You pay for what you get.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>Your satisfaction is our motive. With a team of top consultants, our goal is to ensure that no customer is left unsatisfied.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"meta_title\":\"Middletown DE Garage Doors | Installation, Repair & Service\",\"meta_keyword\":\"garage door installation middletown, garage door repair middletown, garage door service middletown\",\"meta_description\":\"Clark & Sons is Middletown\'s DE trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, & maintenance. Call Now\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-05-21 13:21:13', '2026-02-12 07:10:57', NULL),
(11, 'ocean-city', 'ocean-city-md-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Ocean City\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Ocean City Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"572\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"570\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2805\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Ocean City\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has been Ocean City\\u2019s go-to name for a dependable garage door company. We specialize in residential and commercial garage doors built for durability, performance, and style\\u2014perfect for the unique climate and demands of coastal properties. Whether you\'re upgrading to a modern overhead door or replacing a faulty opener, our solutions are trusted by homeowners and businesses across Ocean City.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our locally serving team understands the needs of Ocean City properties, from boardwalk storefronts to year-round residences. With unmatched craftsmanship and care, we handle everything from complex installations and garage door replacements to broken springs, noisy openers, and emergency repairs.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit our showroom near Ocean City to browse our extensive range of garage door styles, openers, and finishes. Use our interactive virtual visualizer to preview your new door before you commit.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"574\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Boost your property\\u2019s curb appeal and security with a professionally installed garage\\r\\n                                    door. We offer various materials, designs, and customization options to suit your\\r\\n                                    style\\u2014perfectly installed for long-lasting performance, especially in coastal\\r\\n                                    environments like Ocean City.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"573\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>If your garage door is stuck, loud, or off-track, we provide same-day repair service\\r\\n                                    across Ocean City. From broken springs and frayed cables to malfunctioning sensors\\r\\n                                    and openers, our skilled technicians quickly diagnose and fix the issue. Emergency\\r\\n                                    repair services are available 24\\/7.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"567\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>We install, repair, and maintain garage door openers for smooth and secure daily\\r\\n                                    access. Whether you need a basic unit or a smart-enabled system that integrates with\\r\\n                                    your mobile device, we work with all major brands to ensure reliable and quiet\\r\\n                                    operation.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"565\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Keep your garage door operating at its best with our routine maintenance service. Our\\r\\n                                    tune-ups include complete safety inspections, spring and cable checks, track\\r\\n                                    alignment, and lubrication\\u2014helping you avoid costly repairs and extend the life of\\r\\n                                    your door.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"575\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>We install and service heavy-duty, fire-rated hollow metal doors ideal for Ocean\\r\\n                                    City\\u2019s commercial properties. Built for strength, security, and code compliance, our\\r\\n                                    entry systems are a wise choice for retail, hospitality, and warehouse settings.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"568\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Improve operational efficiency and safety with our loading dock solutions. We\\r\\n                                    install, service, and repair dock levelers, bumpers, seals, and shelters\\u2014ensuring\\r\\n                                    your facility stays compliant, functional, and ready to support daily business\\r\\n                                    demands.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"569\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive <br> Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons proudly delivers professional garage door services in Ocean City, MD, backed by over\\r\\n                    60 years of experience. Whether you\'re dealing with a damaged door, planning a complete replacement,\\r\\n                    or booking routine maintenance, our expert team provides fast, reliable solutions tailored to your\\r\\n                    needs and built to withstand Ocean City\\u2019s weather and coastal conditions.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"566\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n    <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\n      Clark and Sons proudly serves homeowners and businesses throughout Ocean City, MD, with dependable garage door installation, <br>repair, and maintenance services. Our local team is always nearby and ready to provide fast, professional support\\u2014whether it\\u2019s a<br> year-round residence, vacation home, or commercial property.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n    <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n        <li><b>Ocean City, Maryland<\\/b>\\r\\n            <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n                <li>Downtown Ocean City <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>Midtown Ocean City <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>North Ocean City <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>West Ocean City <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>Montego Bay <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>Caine Woods <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>Little Salisbury <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>Sunset Island <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>Bayside <\\/li>\\r\\n                <li>Coastal Highway Corridor<\\/li>\\r\\n            <\\/ul>\\r\\n        <\\/li>\\r\\n    <\\/ul>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"bottom-content text-center\\\">We are committed to delivering reliable, responsive, and friendly garage door service throughout the greater Ocean City area and surrounding coastal communities.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"areas_button_name\":\"\",\"areas_button_url\":\"\",\"areas_img\":\"359\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"faq_title\":\"FAQ\'s\",\"faq_sub_title\":\"\",\"faq_img\":\"564\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"why_choose_title\":\"Why Choose Clark and Sons?\",\"why_choose_sub_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_img1\":\"433\",\"why_choose_img2\":\"432\",\"why_choose_img3\":\"431\",\"why_choose_img4\":\"435\",\"why_choose_img5\":\"430\",\"why_choose_img6\":\"434\",\"why_choose_title1\":\"Over 60 Years of Local Expertise\",\"why_choose_title2\":\"Fully Licensed & Insured Professionals\",\"why_choose_title3\":\"Family-Owned and Operated\",\"why_choose_title4\":\"Competitive & Transparent Pricing\",\"why_choose_title5\":\"Conveniently Located Across Delmarva\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"Top-Rated Customer Satisfaction\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"<p>\\r\\nServing Maryland and the Delmarva Peninsula since 1963, we\'re Maryland\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. Our three-generation legacy ensures unmatched experience and reliable service.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"<p>Rest easy knowing your garage door is serviced by skilled, licensed, and fully insured technicians who prioritize quality, safety, and precision in every project.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"<p>As a family-owned business, we put trust, honesty, and personalized care into every job. Your satisfaction and safety are our top priorities.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"<p>We believe in fair pricing without hidden fees. Get clear, upfront quotes, affordable services, and exceptional value with every job.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>With four accessible locations, we\'re always nearby to quickly respond to your garage door installation, maintenance, or repair needs.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>We\\u2019ve earned the trust of thousands of homeowners and businesses through our commitment to quality work, fast response times, and friendly service, which is reflected in our 5-star reviews and loyal customer base.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A  QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"meta_title\":\"Ocean City MD Garage Doors | Installation, Repair & Service\",\"meta_keyword\":\"garage door installation ocean city, garage door repair ocean city, garage door service ocean city\",\"meta_description\":\"Clark & Sons is Ocean City\'s MD trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, & maintenance. Call Now\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-05-21 13:21:13', '2026-03-02 08:04:28', NULL);
