(12, 'ocean-pines', 'ocean-pines-md-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Ocean Pines\' Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Ocean Pines Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"584\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"582\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2806\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Ocean Pines Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has been Ocean Pines\' top choice for a reliable garage door company for over 60 years. We specialize in residential and commercial garage door sales, installation, and repairs, offering expertly crafted solutions that prioritize safety, curb appeal, and long-term performance. Whether you\\u2019re upgrading your home or outfitting a business, we provide dependable service you can trust.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our experienced Ocean Pines team understands the unique needs of local homeowners and property managers. From broken springs and worn cables to modern opener installations and full door replacements, every job is completed with attention to detail, precision, and a commitment to quality.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Stop by our nearby showroom to explore an extensive selection of garage doors and openers. Use our virtual visualizer to preview your new garage door before it\\u2019s installed, making your selection stress-free and straightforward.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"586\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance the look and function of your home or business with our professional garage door installation services. Choose from a wide variety of styles, colors, and materials\\u2014installed with precision and built to withstand the coastal environment of Ocean Pines.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"585\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Dealing with a stuck or noisy garage door? Our Ocean Pines technicians offer same-day repairs for issues like broken springs, damaged rollers, snapped cables, and faulty sensors. We also provide 24\\/7 emergency repair services for urgent problems that can\\u2019t wait.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"579\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Enjoy reliable, secure, and quiet access to your garage with our professional opener installation and repair services. We work with all major brands, including advanced smart openers that connect to your phone for convenient, hands-free operation.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"577\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Prevent unexpected breakdowns and costly repairs with routine maintenance. Our thorough tune-ups include safety checks, balance adjustments, lubrication, and hardware inspections to ensure your garage door system performs reliably and lasts longer.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"587\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Protect your commercial property with heavy-duty, fire-rated hollow metal doors. Built for strength and compliance, our doors are perfect for retail spaces, offices, and industrial sites in Ocean Pines. We provide expert installation and dependable servicing.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"580\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/comm