(13, 'rehoboth-beach', 'rehoboth-beach-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Rehoboth Beach\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Rehoboth Beach Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"596\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"594\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2807\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Rehoboth Beach\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons is the go-to garage door company for homeowners and businesses throughout Rehoboth Beach. We specialize in the sales, installation, and service of high-quality residential and commercial garage doors. Whether you\\u2019re looking for a quiet, durable opener or a stylish new overhead door, we deliver trusted solutions that improve performance, safety, and curb appeal.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>With over six decades of hands-on experience and a locally based team, we proudly provide dependable garage door services across Rehoboth Beach. From cable and spring repairs to full door replacements and smart opener upgrades, our skilled technicians ensure every job is completed with precision and care\\u2014always putting safety and long-term performance first.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Stop by our nearby showroom to explore our wide range of door styles, hardware options, and smart openers. You can even preview your new door using our virtual visualization tool before making a decision.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"598\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Give your home or business a modern, functional upgrade with our expertly installed garage doors. We offer a variety of styles, materials, and custom finishes to match your needs and enhance your property\\u2019s appearance. Every installation is performed by trained technicians using precision tools to ensure a secure, long-lasting fit and polished finish.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"597\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>If your garage door is stuck, noisy, or showing signs of wear, our local team is ready to help. We provide fast, same-day service for broken springs, off-track doors, faulty sensors, damaged rollers, and more. Need help now? Our 24\\/7 emergency repair service is available throughout Rehoboth Beach for your peace of mind.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"591\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Access your garage smoothly and safely with our professional opener services. From basic units to smart systems with smartphone control, we install, repair, and maintain all major brands. We\\u2019ll make sure your garage door opens quietly and reliably\\u2014no matter the season.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"588\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Routine service helps prevent breakdowns and extends the life of your garage door. Our comprehensive tune-ups include safety inspections, spring tension checks, track adjustments, and lubrication. With regular maintenance, you\\u2019ll avoid costly repairs and ensure safe operation year-round.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"599\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Secure your commercial space with rugged, code-co