(16, 'odessa', 'odessa-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Odessa\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly serving Odessa communities for the last 60 years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"623\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"621\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2808\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Your Local Garage Door Experts in Odessa, DE, Serving Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>For over 60 years, Clark & Sons has been a trusted name for garage door installation, repair, and maintenance across the Odessa community. They offer the best solutions in garage door services, from sophisticated contemporary doors to commercial roll-ups, offering professional installation, repair, and maintenance services.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our Odessa residents trust us for advice on weather trends and building regulations when it comes to selecting the right garage door service, thanks to our established trust and professional presence in Odessa, DE. We promise that every detail will be done with precision and care.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Visit one of our local stores to see a range of designs and finishes in person, or use our interactive design tools to picture your new door from the comfort of your home.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"613\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance your home with a beautifully crafted and skillfully installed garage door. We offer a wide range of residential and commercial door types, coatings, and insulation options that are specifically tailored to the design and functionality of your building. Each installation is finished with expert craftsmanship, guar