(17, 'townsend', 'townsend-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Townsend\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Delivering Reliable Garage Door Service to Townsend Families for Over Six Decades<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"635\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"633\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2849\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Serving Townsend with Garage Door Excellence Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>It was never easy to maintain the trust of people in Homeowners and businesses in Townsend. Clark & Sons has been in the market for the past 60 years, offering garage door installation, repair, and maintenance services. We have a team of professionals who can provide you with everything from customized installation to energy-efficient garage doors, sleek contemporary designs, and robust commercial systems.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We have professionals who will deliver the best and most solid, long-lasting outcomes by combining traditional knowledge with contemporary equipment. With Clark & Sons, you can enjoy guaranteed seamless operation and complete peace of mind, whether you\'re upgrading to a modern garage system or repairing a broken spring.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>If you would like to check your own, please visit our local store or refer to our website for more details. Furthermore, if you would like a consultation, please contact us today to upgrade your doors and garage.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"625\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>A precisely fitted garage door may revitalize your house. With Clark &amp; Sons, you will receive high-quality doors, allowing you to choose the material, coating, and insulation levels you prefer. We deal with both residential and commercial structures. <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"624\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repair & Component Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Our Townsend repair crew is prepared to assist if your garage door rattles, stops mid-cycle, or won\'t open. For damaged panels, bent tracks, broken wires, and faulty openers, we provide same-day repair. For pressing problems that cannot wait, emergency services are accessible around the clock. <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"628\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Installation & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Our opener installation and maintenance choices can take your convenience to the next level. We assist you in selecting and configuring the best option for your requirements, from phone-controlled smart openers to silent belt-drive systems.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"627\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Preventive Maintenance & Tune-Ups\",\"description\":\"<p>Our preventative maintenance services will keep your garage door running properly throughout the year. We take care of lubrication, hardware tightening, alignment testing, and safety inspections to help you prolong the life of your door and prevent expensive malfunctions. <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"626\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Fire-rated hollow metal doors designed for durability, safety, and code compliance will safeguard your business property. These entrance systems offer long-lasting protection with minimal upkeep, making them ideal for business b