_title5\":\"Local Presence Across Delmarva\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"A Reputation Built on Satisfaction\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"<p>We have been serving the Delaware market and the Delmarva Peninsula since 1963. We are here to maintain our legacy of three generations of dedicated service.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"<p>With Clark &amp; Sons, you get professional technicians who ensure everything is done safely. All our technicians are licensed and well-trained, so they offer the best services.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"<p>It has over 60 years of legacy. Yes is a family-owned company. We offer our customers our services with honesty, transparency, and genuine customer care on every project.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"<p>We don\\u2019t trick our customers with any hidden charges. Our pricing is highly competitive, with upfront quotes available. Hence, we ensure that you to maintain transparency from our end to you.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>With four nearby offices, our teams respond quickly to Townsend and the surrounding communities whenever you need assistance.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>You can check our feedback given by our customers. They have rated us with five stars because they loved our consistent quality, reliability, and customer-first service.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A  QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"meta_title\":\"Townsend DE Garage Doors