(18, 'smyrna', 'smyrna-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Smyrna\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Serving the Smyrna Community with Pride for Over Six Decades<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"647\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"645\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2850\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Trusted Garage Door Professionals in Smyrna, DE Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>For nearly 60 years, homeowners and businesses in Smyrna have trusted Clark & Sons for reliable garage door installation, repair, and maintenance. Our professional team at Smyrna and surrounding areas of Delaware offers everything from traditional carriage-style garage doors to modern, insulated steel options. We also provide installation, repair, and servicing solutions that combine visual beauty with everyday dependability.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>When you\\u2019re looking for energy-efficient door enhancements and also about replacing your old system or troubleshooting a stuck opener, we guarantee that your garage runs as smoothly and safely as the day it was built.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>You can simply visit our nearest store to see our products in person or use our digital door design tools from the comfort of your home to check out the next makeover of your living place. \\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"637\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Our professional team offers skilled installation services to transform your home into a contemporary look. We provide installation services for all ranges of styles, from rustic wood tones to sleek modern finishes. Once decided, our team installs each door to the greatest standards, ensuring superior insulation and smooth functioning for many years to come.  <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"636\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repair & Component Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>If your garage door malfunctions, makes strange noises, or won\'t open, our Smyrna team has got you covered. For same-day repairs, our Smyrna garage door professionals come on time and have replacement parts for most major brands. In the case of an emergency, you can get access to our 24\\/7 emergency service.  <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"640\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Installation & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>An intelligent, silent garage door opener will increase your convenience. We take care of everything, including setup and connection with security systems and mobile apps. Our staff makes sure your opener runs quietly and effectively, giving your everyday routine more comfort and control.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"639\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Tune-Ups & Preventive Maintenance\",\"description\":\"<p>If minor problems are ignored, they might become major fixes. In order to assist you in preventing downtime and costly malfunctions, our maintenance service comprises system checks, lubrication, balance adjustments, and safety testing.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"638\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Take a look at commercial-grade hollow metal doors, perfect for strength and safety. They safeguard your company easily. These doors are a perfect selection for offices, warehouses, and other industrial buildings where they need fire-rated and code-compliant doors. \\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"643\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Installation & Maintenance\",\"description\":\"<p>Use our professional dock solutions to streamline your operations. We install and maintain bumpers, seals, and dock levelers that enhance productivity, lessen wear, and preserve your facility\'s adherence to safety regulations.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"644\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Comprehensive Garage Door <br> Services in Smyrna, DE\",\"description\":\"<p>Garage door maintenance should be easy, stress-free, and long-lasting, in our opinion at Clark &amp; Sons. Because of this, our whole range of services includes everything from brand-new installations to continuing maintenance plans meant to keep your door operating at its best.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"641\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quo