(21, 'magnolia', 'magnolia-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Magnolia\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Magnolia Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"683\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"681\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2853\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Magnolia\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark & Sons has long been Magnolia\\u2019s go-to garage door company for installation, repair, and maintenance services, recognized for delivering reliable products and exceptional workmanship. Whether you require a modern insulated door for a newly built home, a durable commercial unit designed for daily operation, or a seamless opener upgrade to enhance accessibility, our team ensures superior craftsmanship and dependable performance.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With 60+ years of hands-on experience and a dedicated team of local professionals, we deliver reliable and comprehensive garage door services throughout Magnolia. From intricate installations to urgent spring replacements and advanced smart opener upgrades, every project is completed with a commitment to precision, safety, and long-term performance.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Visit our nearby showroom to explore our extensive selection of garage doors, openers, and accessories. Our virtual visualization tools allow you to preview how your new door will enhance your home\\u2019s appearance before making a final decision.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"673\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance your home with a new garage door that seamlessly combines functionality and aesthetics. We offer a range of finishes, including steel, aluminum, composite, and wood-look options, in various colors and insulation levels. Every installation is meticulously designed to ensure longevity, quiet operation, and long-term curb appeal. <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"672\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>When your garage door stops functioning, downtime is not an option. Our same-day repair service in Magnolia provides prompt support for broken springs, damaged cables, malfunctioning openers, and compromised panels. For urgent situations, our 24-hour emergency service ensures your home or facility remains safe and secure at all times.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"678\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Enjoy effortless access with a professionally installed opener. From belt-drive systems to Wi-Fi-enabled smart technology, we\\u2019ll match you with the perfect opener and ensure smooth, whisper-quiet performance.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"676\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Prevent unexpected issues before they arise with our comprehensive preventive maintenance services. Our detailed tune-ups include balance assessments, track alignment, safety system inspections, and full lubrication of all moving components. These maintenance plans are specifically designed to prolong the lifespan of your garage door, enhance daily performance, and reduce the likelihood of costly repairs.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"675\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Safeguard your commercial property with high-durability, fire-rated hollow metal doors designed for long-term security and dependable performance. Ideal for office buildings, retail establishments, and warehouse facilities, these doors provide superior protection in demanding environments. We supply, install, and service entry systems engineered to comply with local building codes and all applicable safety standards.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"679\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance safety and operational efficiency at your facility with our comprehensive dock equipment services. We install and maintain dock levelers, bumpers, seals, and shelters to support streamlined loading operations and ensure compliance with all safety requirements. Our technicians work with precision and efficiency, minimizing downtime while improving your facility\\u2019s overall workflow.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"680\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive <br> Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Clark &amp; Sons has provided reliable, expert garage door services in Magnolia for more than 60 years. Whether you are installing a new door, replacing worn components, or scheduling preventative maintenance, our skilled team delivers workmanship that meets the highest industry standards. We are dedicated to helping you protect your property, enhance curb appeal, and enjoy seamless, worry-free garage door performance year-round.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"677\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\n Clark & Sons proudly supports homeowners and businesses throughout Magnolia, DE, with reliable garage door installation, repair, and maintenance services. <br>Our local team remains close by and readily available to deliver prompt, professional assistance whenever you need it.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n <li><b>Magnolia, Delaware<\\/b>\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n<li>Barkers Landing<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Brookdale Heights<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Brookfield<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Del Haven Estates<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Hunters Run<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Longacre Village<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Magnolia Proper<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Rising Sun\\u2013Lebanon<\\/li>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n <\\/li>\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"bottom-content text-center\\\">We are dedicated to providing dependable, responsive, and friendly garage door service throughout the greater Magnoli