friendly service, which is reflected in our 5-star reviews and loyal customer base.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A  QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"meta_title\":\"Magnolia DE Garage Doors | Installation, Repair & Service\",\"meta_keyword\":\"garage door installation magnolia, garage door repair magnolia, garage door service magnolia\",\"meta_description\":\"Clark & Sons is Magnolia\'s DE trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, & maintenance. Call Now\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-05-21 13:21:13', '2026-02-12 06:31:04', NULL);
