(31, 'harrington', 'harrington-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Harrington\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Harrington Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"2714\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"2712\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2854\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Harrington\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has proudly served as a trusted garage door company in Harrington for more than six decades. We provide professional garage door installation, repair, and service for residential and commercial properties throughout the area. From durable overhead doors to custom residential designs and reliable commercial solutions, we deliver doors built for performance, safety, and long-term value.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With over 60 years of hands-on experience and a team of highly trained local technicians, we provide dependable garage door services tailored to the needs of Harrington homeowners and businesses. Whether it\\u2019s a complete installation, urgent repair, spring replacement, or opener upgrade, every project is completed with precision, safety, and attention to detail.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Visit one of our nearby showrooms to explore our wide selection of residential and commercial garage doors, openers, and accessories. Our visualization tools allow you to see exactly how your new garage door will look before making a decision.<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"2717\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance your home or business with a professionally installed garage door de