low metal doors. These entry systems are ideal for offices, warehouses, and retail spaces. We provide professional installation and service that meets safety standards and local building requirements.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2710\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Installation & Maintenance\",\"description\":\"<p>Improve efficiency and safety with professional loading dock equipment services. We install and maintain dock levelers, seals, shelters, and bumpers to support smooth daily operations and minimize downtime for your facility.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2711\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has delivered reliable garage door services in Harrington for over 60 years. Whether you need a new garage door installed, fast repairs, or routine service, our experienced technicians are committed to quality workmanship and dependable results. We help protect your property, enhance curb appeal, and ensure smooth garage door operation year-round.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"2708\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub