(22, 'newark', 'newark-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Newark\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Newark Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"693\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"691\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2855\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Newark\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark & Sons has been the trusted choice for residents and businesses in Newark for more than 60 years, delivering reliable, high-quality garage door installation, repair, and maintenance services. From modern insulated steel systems to the replacement of aging wood doors, our work reflects a commitment to durability, safety, and enhanced curb appeal. Every project is completed with exceptional craftsmanship and long-lasting performance in mind.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With 60+ years of practical experience and a dedicated team of local experts, we deliver dependable garage door services right here in Newark. Whether handling intricate installations, urgent spring replacements, or advanced smart opener upgrades, we complete every project with a strong focus on precision, safety, and long-term reliability.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Visit our local showroom to explore a wide range of garage doors, openers, and accessories. Our virtual visualization tools allow you to preview how your selected door will complement your home\\u2019s exterior before making a final decision.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"695\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance your home or commercial property with a garage door that reflects 