rage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Safeguard your commercial property with durable, fire-rated hollow metal doors engineered for long-lasting security and performance. Ideal for office buildings, retail centers, and warehouse facilities, these doors provide dependable protection in demanding environments. We install and service entry systems that fully comply with local building codes and all applicable safety standards.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"689\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Enhance the safety and operational efficiency of your facility with our expert dock equipment services. We install and maintain dock levelers, bumpers, seals, and shelters to support smooth loading operations and ensure full compliance with safety regulations. Our technicians work with precision and efficiency, minimizing disruption while improving your facility\\u2019s overall workflow.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"690\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive <br>Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Clark &amp; Sons has been a trusted provider of garage door services in Newark for more than 60 years. Whether you are installing a new door, replacing worn or damaged components, or scheduling routine maintenance, our experienced technicians complete every project with the highest level of craftsmanship and care. Our goal is to help you safeguard your home, enhance curb appeal, and enjoy reliable, worry-free garage door performance throughout the year.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"687\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\n Clark & Sons proudly serves homeowners and businesses throughout Newark, DE, with reliable garage door installation, repair, and maintenance services. <br>Our local team remains close at hand and fully prepared to deliver prompt, professional support whenever you need it.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n <li><b>Newark, Delaware<\\/b>\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n<li>Academy Hill<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Arbour Park<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Cherry Hill<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Christianstead<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>College Park<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Covered Bridge Farms<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Devon<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Fairfield<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Nottingham Green<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Ridgewood Glen<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Scottfield<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Silverbrook<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>West Newark<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Williamhurst<\\/li>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n <\\/li>\\r\\