(37, 'delmar', 'delmar-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Delmar\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>\\r\\nProudly Serving Delmar Families for Over 60 Years\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"2736\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"2738\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2856\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Delmar\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>\\r\\nClark and Sons is proud to be the premier garage door company in Delmar residents and business owners have relied on for quality and reliability for over six decades. Our expertise lies in the professional sales, precision installation, and repair of residential and commercial doors. Whether you are searching for a whisper-quiet brilliant opener, a stylish residential upgrade, or rugged overhead doors that industrial facilities require for daily operations, our specialized solutions are engineered for maximum safety and longevity.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nWith a legacy spanning three generations, our local team brings unmatched technical skill to every garage door service in Delmar. From complex system overhauls to rapid spring replacements and modern security upgrades, we treat every property with the highest level of professionalism and care.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nWe invite you to visit our local showroom to explore our diverse range of garage doors, openers, and accessories. Our digital design tools allow you to visualize exactly how a new door will enhance your Delmar property\\u2019s curb appeal before the work even begins.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"2739\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\