arkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>\\r\\nBeyond the garage, we secure your facility with high-grade hollow metal doors. These fire-rated systems offer superior protection for retail stores, schools, and offices throughout Delmar, ensuring your business stays compliant with all local safety and building codes.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2744\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>\\r\\nOptimize safety and efficiency at your facility with our professional dock equipment services. We install and maintain dock levelers, bumpers, seals, and shelters to ensure smooth operations and compliance with safety regulations. Our technicians work efficiently to minimize disruptions and improve daily workflow.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2745\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive <br> Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>\\r\\nAt Clark and Sons, we offer a comprehensive suite of garage door services in Delmar, backed by over sixty years of field experience. Whether you are building a new home, renovating a commercial warehouse, or simply need a routine safety inspection, our technicians ensure your systems operate at peak performance.\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\