(32, 'milton', 'milton-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Milton\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Milton Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"2691\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"2689\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2857\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Milton\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has stood as the premier garage door company Milton homeowners and business owners have relied on for quality and reliability for over six decades. Our expertise lies in the seamless sales, professional installation, and expert upkeep of high-performance entry systems. Whether you are searching for a whisper-quiet smart opener, a stylish residential upgrade, or rugged overhead garage doors that industrial facilities require for daily operations, our specialized solutions are engineered for maximum safety and longevity.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With a family legacy spanning three generations, our local technicians bring unparalleled technical expertise to every garage door service in Milton. From complex mechanical overhauls to rapid-response spring replacements and modern security enhancements, we treat every property with the utmost professionalism and care.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We invite you to explore our local showroom to view our diverse collection of garage doors, openers, and accessories. Our innovative digital design tools allow you to visualize exactly how a new installation will elevate your property\\u2019s curb appeal before the project even begins.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"2693\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installa