":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Beyond the garage, we secure your facility with industrial-grade hollow metal entry doors. These fire-rated systems offer top-tier protection for retail outlets, schools, and offices throughout Milton, ensuring your business remains compliant with all local fire codes and safety standards. <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2687\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Installation & Maintenance\",\"description\":\"<p>We assist Milton businesses in optimizing their distribution and receiving bays. Our technicians install and maintain heavy-duty dock levelers, seals, and shelters. By keeping your dock equipment in optimal condition, we help you enhance workplace safety and streamline overall operational efficiency.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2688\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>At Clark and Sons, we deliver a full spectrum of garage door services in Milton, backed by sixty years of proven field experience. Whether you are constructing a new home, upgrading a commercial warehouse, or simply require a routine safety tune-up, our technicians ensure your systems function at peak performance.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"2685\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\nClark and Sons is honored to be a cornerstone of the Milton community, providing the garage doors Milton homeowners and <br> facility managers trust for daily performance. We are ready to serve you throughout the greater Milton area.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n <li><b>Milton, Delaware<\\/b>\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n <li>Historic Downtown Milton<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Cannery Village<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Paynter\\u2019s Mill<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Woodfield Preserve<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Wagamon\\u2019s West Shore<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Heritage Creek<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Pemberton Pond<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Diamond Pond<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Broadkill River District<\\/li>\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n <\\/li>\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"bottom-content text-center\\\">Our dedicated team is committed to delivering responsive, high-quality garage door solutions throughout Milton and its surrounding neighborhoods.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"areas_button_name\":\"\",\"areas_button_url\":\"\",\"areas_img\":\"359\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"faq_title\":\"FAQ\'s\",\"faq_sub_title\":\"\",\"faq_img\":\"2683\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"why_choose_title\":\"Why Choose Clark and Sons?\",\"why_choose_sub_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_img1\":\"433\",\"why_choose_img2\":\"431\",\"why_choose_img3\":\"432\",\"why_choose_img4\":\"435\",\"why_choose_img5\":\"430\",\"why_choose_img6\":\"434\",\"why_choose_title1\":\"Over 60 Years of Local Expertise\",\"why_choose_title2\":\"Family-Owned and Operated\",\"why_choose_title3\":\"Fully Licensed & Insured Professionals\",\"why_choose_title4\":\"Competitive & Transparent Pricing\",\"why_choose_title5\":\"Conveniently Located Across Delmarva\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"Top-Rated Customer Satisfaction\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"<p>Serving Delaware and the Delmarva Peninsula since 1963, we\'re Delaware\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. Our three-generation legacy ensures unmatched experience and reliable service.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"<p>As a family-owned business, we put trust, honesty, and personalized care into every job. Your satisfaction and safety are our top priorities.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"<p>Rest easy knowing your garage door is serviced by skilled, licensed, and fully insured technicians who prioritize quality, safety, and precision in every project.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"<p>We believe in fair pricing without hidden fees. Get clear, upfront quotes, affordable services, and exceptional value with every job.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>With four accessible locations, we\'re always nearby to quickly respond to your garage door installation, maintenance, or repair needs.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>We\\u2019ve earned the trust of thousands of homeowners and businesses through our commitment to quality work, fast response times, and friendly service, which is reflected in our 5-star reviews and loyal customer base.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A  QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"meta_title\":\"MiltonDE Garage Doors | Installation, Repair & Service\",\"meta_keyword\":\"garage door installation milton, garage door repair milton, garage door service milton\",\"meta_description\":\"Clark & Sons is Milton\'s DE trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, & maintenance. Call Now\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-05-21 13:21:13', '2026-02-12 06:32:41', NULL),
(33, 'milford', 'milford-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Milford\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>Proudly Serving Milford Families for Over 60 Years<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"2679\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"2677\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2858\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Milford\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>Clark and Sons has earned its reputation as a leading garage door company in Milford by delivering dependable service for more than six decades. We specialize in professional garage door installation, expert repairs, and ongoing service for both residential and commercial properties. Whether you\\u2019re upgrading your home with modern overhead garage doors that homeowners trust or installing heavy-duty commercial systems, our solutions are built for durability, safety, and long-term performance.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With three generations of experience behind us, our local technicians bring proven expertise to every garage door service in Milford. From full system replacements and spring repairs to opener upgrades and safety improvements, we treat every property with care, precision, and respect.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We welcome you to visit one of our nearby showrooms to explore our extensive lineup of garage doors, openers, and accessories. Our interactive design tools let you preview how a new garage door will enhance your Milford home or business before installation begins.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"2681\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Upgrade your property with professional garage do