rvice\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Beyond the garage, we secure your facility with high-grade hollow metal entry doors. These fire-rated systems offer superior protection for retail stores, schools, and offices throughout New Castle, ensuring your business stays compliant with all local safety and building codes. <\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2700\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Installation & Maintenance\",\"description\":\"<p>We help New Castle businesses optimize their shipping and receiving areas. Our technicians install and maintain industrial dock levelers, seals, and shelters. By keeping your dock equipment in top shape, we help you improve workplace safety and operational efficiency.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2701\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>At Clark and Sons, we offer a comprehensive suite of garage door services in New Castle, backed by over sixty years of field experience. Whether you are building a new home, renovating a commercial warehouse, or simply need a routine safety inspection, our technicians ensure your systems operate at peak performance.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"2698\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\nClark and Sons is proud to be a staple in the New Castle community, providing top-tier garage door installation, repair, and <br>maintenance services for New Castle homeowners and facility managers. We are ready to serve you wherever you are located in the region.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n <li><b>New Castle, Delaware<\\/b>\\r\\n <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n <li>Historic New Castle<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Wilmington Manor<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Manor Park<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Swanwyck<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Dunleith<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Rambleton Acres<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Penn Valley<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Jefferson Farms<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Dobbinsville<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>Washington Park<\\/li>\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n <\\/li>\\r\\n <\\/ul>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"bottom-content text-center\\\">Our team is dedicated to providing responsive, high-quality garage door solutions throughout New Castle and its surrounding neighborhoods.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"areas_button_name\":\"\",\"areas_button_url\":\"\",\"areas_img\":\"359\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"faq_title\":\"FAQ\'s\",\"faq_sub_title\":\"\",\"faq_img\":\"2696\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"why_choose_title\":\"Why Choose Clark and Sons?\",\"why_choose_sub_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_img1\":\"433\",\"why_choose_img2\":\"431\",\"why_choose_img3\":\"432\",\"why_choose_img4\":\"435\",\"why_choose_img5\":\"430\",\"why_choose_img6\":\"434\",\"why_choose_title1\":\"Over 60 Years of Local Expertise\",\"why_choose_title2\":\"Family-Owned and Operated\",\"why_choose_title3\":\"Fully Licensed & Insured Professionals\",\"why_choose_title4\":\"Competitive & Transparent Pricing\",\"why_choose_title5\":\"Conveniently Located Across Delmarva\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"Top-Rated Customer Satisfaction\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"<p>Serving Delaware and the Delmarva Peninsula since 1963, we\'re Delaware\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. Our three-generation legacy ensures unmatched experience and reliable service.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"<p>As a family-owned business, we put trust, honesty, and personalized care into every job. Your satisfaction and safety are our top priorities.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"<p>Rest easy knowing your garage door is serviced by skilled, licensed, and fully insured technicians who prioritize quality, safety, and precision in every project.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"<p>We believe in fair pricing without hidden fees. Get clear, upfront quotes, affordable services, and exceptional value with every job.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>With four accessible locations, we\'re always nearby to quickly respond to your garage door installation, maintenance, or repair needs.<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>We\\u2019ve earned the trust of thousands of homeowners and businesses through our commitment to quality work, fast response times, and friendly service, which is reflected in our 5-star reviews and loyal customer base.<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A  QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"meta_title\":\"New Castle DE Garage Doors | Installation, Repair &  Service\",\"meta_keyword\":\"garage door installation new castle, garage door repair new castle, garage door service new castle\",\"meta_description\":\"Clark &  Sons is New Castle\'s DE trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, & maintenance. Call Now\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2025-05-21 13:21:13', '2026-02-12 06:33:22', NULL),
(36, 'claymont', 'claymont-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Claymont\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>\\r\\nProudly Serving Claymont Families for Over 60 Years\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"2724\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"2725\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2847\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Claymont\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>\\r\\nClark and Sons has been a trusted garage door company in Claymont for more than six decades, delivering reliable solutions for both residential and commercial properties. From classic overhead garage doors to modern, insulated designs, we specialize in garage door installation, repair, and service in Claymont tailored to the unique needs of homeowners and businesses. Our team helps you choose the right door style, opener, and system for long-term performance and everyday convenience.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nWith over 60 years of industry experience, our skilled technicians provide dependable garage door service in Claymont backed by craftsmanship, safety, and attention to detail. Whether you need emergency garage door repair, a complete door replacement, or a smart opener upgrade, we complete every project with precision and care to ensure smooth, secure operation.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nVisit our nearby showroom to explore a wide selection of residential and commercial doors, openers, and accessories. Our visualization tools allow you to preview how your new garage door will look on your property before installation.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"2727\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\"