(38, 'hockessin', 'hockessin-de-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Hockessin\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>\\r\\nProudly Serving Hockessin Families for Over 60 Years\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"2748\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"2749\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2861\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Hockessin\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p>\\r\\nClark and Sons is the garage door company in Hockessin that homeowners and businesses continue to trust for dependable service, premium products, and long-term value. For over six decades, we have specialized in the sales, installation, and maintenance of high-performance garage doors designed to enhance security, convenience, and curb appeal. Whether you\\u2019re investing in new residential garage doors, upgrading overhead doors for a commercial property, or replacing an aging opener, our solutions are built for reliability and everyday performance.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nAs a third-generation, family-run business, our technicians bring deep hands-on knowledge to every garage door service in Hockessin. From precision garage door installation to fast-response garage door repair, we approach every project with attention to detail and respect for your property.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nWe welcome you to visit our showroom to explore our wide range of garage doors, openers, and accessories. Using modern design visualization tools, you can see how a new garage door will complement your home or business before installation even begins.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"2751\",\"system_img1\":\"21\",\"system_img2\":\"22\",\"system_img3\":\"24\",\"system_img4\":\"23\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installati