(42, 'cambridge', 'cambridge-md-garage-doors', 1, 'service-area', '{\"checked\":1,\"banner_title\":\"Cambridge\\u2019s Most Trusted Garage Door Company\",\"banner_subtitle\":\"\",\"banner_description\":\"<p>\\r\\nProudly Serving Cambridge Families for Over 60 Years\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"banner_img\":\"2880\",\"banner_img_1100x480\":\"2877\",\"mobile_banner_img\":\"2878\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"system_setting_title\":\"Cambridge\\u2019s Garage Door Experts Since 1963\",\"system_sub_title\":\"\",\"system_setting_description\":\"<p> Clark and Sons has proudly served the Cambridge community for over six decades, delivering dependable garage door solutions designed for safety, durability, and long-term performance. As a trusted garage door company in Cambridge, we specialize in the sales, installation, and repair of residential and commercial doors. From modern overhead doors to custom replacements, we provide solutions that enhance both functionality and curb appeal.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our experienced technicians understand the needs of both Cambridge homeowners and business owners. Every project is handled with precision and care. Whether it\\u2019s a new garage door installation, a time-sensitive repair, or an upgrade to a smart opener system. We focus on quality workmanship, reliable service, and results you can trust. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Visit one of our nearby showrooms to explore a wide range of garage doors, openers, and finishes. With our virtual design tools, you can preview how your new garage door will look on your Cambridge property before installation. <\\/p>\",\"system_img\":\"2882\",\"system_img1\":\"2883\",\"system_img2\":\"2884\",\"system_img3\":\"2885\",\"system_img4\":\"2886\",\"title1\":\"Over 61 years <br>of experience\",\"title2\":\"Fully Insured\",\"title3\":\"Competitive <br> Prices\",\"title4\":\"Family Owned\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Garage Door Installation & Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>Upgrade your Cambridge home or business with expertly installed garage doors built for lasting performance. We offer a wide selection of residential and commercial garage doors in various materials, styles, and insulation options. Our professional installers ensure precise alignment, smooth operation, and long-term reliability.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2881\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Residential Garage Doors\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Repairs & Parts Replacement\",\"description\":\"<p>If your garage door is malfunctioning, our team provides prompt garage door repair in Cambridge. We service broken springs, damaged panels, frayed cables, off-track doors, and faulty openers. With 24\\/7 emergency repair availability, you can count on fast, dependable support when it matters most.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2874\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Repairs\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Opener Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Access your garage with ease using a professionally installed or serviced opener system. Whether you need a standard model or a Wi-Fi-enabled brilliant opener, we provide expert solutions tailored to your lifestyle and budget\\u2014ensuring smooth, quiet, and secure operation.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2872\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/residential\\/openers\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Openers\"},{\"title\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\",\"description\":\"<p>Keep your garage door in top shape with our preventative maintenance services. We perform thorough inspections, safety checks, and tune-ups, including balancing, lubrication, and tightening of hardware. Prevent issues before they happen and extend your door\\u2019s lifespan.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2871\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/service-and-repair\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Garage Door Maintenance & Service\"},{\"title\":\"Hollow Metal Entry Door Systems\",\"description\":\"<p>Protect your commercial property with durable, fire-rated hollow metal entry doors designed for security and heavy use. Ideal for warehouses, offices, and retail facilities, these systems are installed and maintained to meet all safety and building code requirements.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2875\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/commercial\\/hollow-metal-doors\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Hollow Metal Door\"},{\"title\":\"Loading Dock Equipment Services\",\"description\":\"<p>Improve efficiency and safety at your facility with professional loading dock equipment services. We install and service dock levelers, shelters, seals, and bumpers to ensure smooth operations, minimize downtime, and maintain compliance with workplace safety standards.<\\/p>\",\"img\":\"2876\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\/loading-dock\\/\",\"urltitle\":\"Loading Dock Equipment\"}]', '{\"title\":\"Our Comprehensive  <br> Garage Door Services\",\"description\":\"<p>At Clark and Sons, we\\u2019ve provided professional garage door services in Cambridge for over 60 years. From expert installations and emergency repairs to routine maintenance, our team delivers cost-effective solutions that keep your garage door operating safely and efficiently. We\\u2019re committed to protecting your property and ensuring dependable performance year-round.<\\/p>\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"door_title\":\"Common Garage\",\"door_sub_title\":\"Door Problems\",\"garage_door_description\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\/p>\",\"garage_img\":\"2873\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"quote_title\":\"Contact Us Today!\",\"quotesub_title\":\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\",\"quote_button_name\":\"Request Help Here\",\"quote_button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"quotecall_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"quotecall_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"quote_desc\":\"\"}', '{\"resi_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"resi_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"areas_title\":\"Areas We Proudly Serve\",\"areas_sub_title\":\"<div class=\\\"area-top-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"top\\\">\\r\\n    Clark and Sons proudly serves homeowners and businesses throughout Cambridge, MD, with reliable garage door\\r\\n    installation, repair, and maintenance services.<br> Our local technicians are always nearby and ready to help.\\r\\n  <\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"area-we-serve-location\\\">\\r\\n  <ul class=\\\"two-column-list\\\">\\r\\n    <li>\\r\\n      <b>\\r\\n        Cambridge, Maryland\\r\\n      <\\/b>\\r\\n      <ul class=\\\"sub-list\\\">\\r\\n        <li>Algonquin<\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>Cambridge<\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>Church Creek<\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>Choptank River Area<\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>Downtown Cambridge<\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>East Cambridge<\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>Hambrooks<\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>Longboat Estates<\\/li>\\r\\n        <li>West End<\\/li>\\r\\n      <\\/ul>\\r\\n    <\\/li>\\r\\n  <\\/ul>\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"bottom-content text-center\\\">\\r\\n    We are committed to delivering reliable, responsive, and friendly garage door service throughout the Cambridge area\\r\\n    and its surrounding Eastern Shore communities.\\r\\n  <\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"areas_button_name\":\"\",\"areas_button_url\":\"\",\"areas_img\":\"359\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"faq_title\":\"FAQ\'s\",\"faq_sub_title\":\"\",\"faq_img\":\"2879\"}', '{\"checked\":1,\"why_choose_title\":\"Why Choose Clark and Sons?\",\"why_choose_sub_title\":\"\",\"why_choose_img1\":\"433\",\"why_choose_img2\":\"432\",\"why_choose_img3\":\"431\",\"why_choose_img4\":\"435\",\"why_choose_img5\":\"430\",\"why_choose_img6\":\"434\",\"why_choose_title1\":\"Over 60 Years of Local Expertise\",\"why_choose_title2\":\"Fully Licensed & Insured Professionals\",\"why_choose_title3\":\"Family-Owned and Operated\",\"why_choose_title4\":\"Competitive & Transparent Pricing\",\"why_choose_title5\":\"Conveniently Located Across Delmarva\",\"why_choose_title6\":\"Top-Rated Customer Satisfaction\",\"why_choose_description1\":\"<p>\\r\\nServing Maryland and the Delmarva Peninsula since 1963, we\'re Maryland\\u2019s oldest independent garage door company. Our three-generation legacy ensures unmatched experience and reliable service.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description2\":\"<p>\\r\\nRest easy knowing your garage door is serviced by skilled, licensed, and fully insured technicians who prioritize quality, safety, and precision in every project.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description3\":\"<p>\\r\\nAs a family-owned business, we put trust, honesty, and personalized care into every job. Your satisfaction and safety are our top priorities.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description4\":\"<p>\\r\\nWe believe in fair pricing without hidden fees. Get clear, upfront quotes, affordable services, and exceptional value with every job.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description5\":\"<p>\\r\\nWith four accessible locations, we\'re always nearby to quickly respond to your garage door installation, maintenance, or repair needs.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"why_choose_description6\":\"<p>\\r\\nWe\\u2019ve earned the trust of thousands of homeowners and businesses through our commitment to quality work, fast response times, and friendly service, which is reflected in our 5-star reviews and loyal customer base.\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}', NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"calltoaction_title\":\"Don\'t Try to Fix it Yourself!\",\"calltosub_title\":\"\",\"button_name\":\"GET A  QUOTE\",\"button_url\":\"#getafreequote\",\"call_button_name\":\"CALL NOW\",\"call_button_url\":\"tel:+18004793667\",\"call_button_desc\":\"It\'s crucial to entrust the repair of faulty garage doors to a skilled technician. Issues with cables or springs can pose significant hazards without proper expertise. With our extensive experience and specialized equipment, rest assured that all problems will be safely resolved.\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{\"checked\":1,\"meta_title\":\"Cambridge MD Garage Doors | Installation, Repair & Service\",\"meta_keyword\":\"garage door installation cambridge , garage door repair cambridge , garage door service cambridge\",\"meta_description\":\"Clark & Sons is Cambridge\'s MD  trusted garage door expert with 60+ years of experience, offering residential and commercial installation, repair, & maintenance. Call Now\"}', 5, 5, NULL, '2026-02-24 07:47:28', '2026-02-24 10:54:28', NULL);
