(1, '15', '1', '1', '{\"image\":\"15\",\"alt_name\":\"\",\"link\":\"None\",\"custom_link\":\"\",\"target_blank\":\"\",\"i_alignment\":\"\"}', '{\"img_width\":\"\",\"img_max_width\":\"\",\"img_height\":\"\"}', '{\"bg_color\":\"\"}', '{\"class\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"}', 5, 5, 5, '2024-05-22 00:00:30', '2024-05-22 00:16:50', '2024-05-22 00:16:50'),
(2, '12', '1', '2', '{\"text_content\":\"<p>Randy Stratton Wedding Officiant specializes in creating personalized and heartfelt wedding ceremonies. Whether you prefer a traditional, contemporary, or themed ceremony, Randy collaborates closely with couples to develop a unique script that reflects their love story. His services go beyond officiating, offering guidance on vows, readings, and ceremony logistics to ensure a seamless and memorable experience.<\\/p>\",\"t_alignment\":\"\"}', NULL, '{\"bg_color\":\"\",\"bg_img\":\"\",\"bg_size\":\"Select\",\"bg_position\":\"Select\",\"bg_repeate\":\"Select\"}', '{\"class\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"}', 5, 5, 5, '2024-05-22 00:00:34', '2024-05-22 00:16:50', '2024-05-22 00:16:50'),
(3, '15', '1', '1', '{\"image\":\"16\",\"alt_name\":\"\",\"link\":\"None\",\"custom_link\":\"\",\"target_blank\":\"\",\"i_alignment\":\"\"}', '{\"img_width\":\"\",\"img_max_width\":\"\",\"img_height\":\"\"}', '{\"bg_color\":\"\"}', '{\"class\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"}', 5, 5, 5, '2024-05-22 00:04:41', '2024-05-22 00:05:27', '2024-05-22 00:05:27'),
(4, '15', '2', '1', '{\"image\":\"18\",\"alt_name\":\"\",\"link\":\"None\",\"custom_link\":\"\",\"target_blank\":\"\",\"i_alignment\":\"\"}', '{\"img_width\":\"\",\"img_max_width\":\"\",\"img_height\":\"\"}', '{\"bg_color\":\"\"}', '{\"class\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"}', 5, 5, 5, '2024-05-22 00:05:59', '2024-05-22 00:16:59', '2024-05-22 00:16:59'),
(5, '15', '2', '2', '{\"image\":\"12\",\"alt_name\":\"\",\"link\":\"None\",\"custom_link\":\"\",\"target_blank\":\"\",\"i_alignment\":\"\"}', '{\"img_width\":\"\",\"img_max_width\":\"\",\"img_height\":\"\"}', '{\"bg_color\":\"\"}', '{\"class\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"}', 5, 5, 5, '2024-05-22 00:06:03', '2024-05-22 00:16:59', '2024-05-22 00:16:59'),
(6, '12', '2', '3', '{\"text_content\":\"<p>As the weather warms up and the days are longer, many couples opt for a more casual approach to their wedding and request their Ceremony to be done outside in their backyard or one that may be special to them. Casual backyard weddings are charming and memorable; however, you need to have a contingency plan should bad weather be in the forecast.<\\/p>\",\"t_alignment\":\"left\"}', NULL, '{\"bg_color\":\"\",\"bg_img\":\"\",\"bg_size\":\"Select\",\"bg_position\":\"Select\",\"bg_repeate\":\"Select\"}', '{\"class\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"}', 5, 5, 5, '2024-05-22 00:06:08', '2024-05-22 00:16:59', '2024-05-22 00:16:59'),
