(1, 'Service Areas | Clark and Sons', NULL, 'Explore Clark & Sons service areas across Maryland and Delaware. Providing reliable garage door installation, repair, and service wherever you are. Call Now', 'Areas We Proudly Serve', '<div class=\"area-top-content text-center\">\r\n  <p class=\"top\">\r\n    At Clark and Sons Garage Doors, we\'re committed to providing timely, reliable service across the entire Maryland and Delaware. With four conveniently located offices, we\'re always nearby and ready to assist you with expert garage door installations, repairs, and maintenance.\r\n  </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"parent-location\">\r\n  <div class=\"proud-area-we-serve-location section-one\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"location-title\">\r\n      Delaware\r\n    </h2>\r\n    <div class=\"line-area\">\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"delaware-section\">\r\n      <ul class=\"two-column-list\">\r\n        <li>\r\n          <h5>\r\n            New Castle County\r\n          </h5>\r\n          <ul class=\"sub-list\">\r\n            <li>\r\n              Bear\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li class=\"service-button\">\r\n              <a href=\"https://clarkandsonsdoors.com/service-areas/claymont-de-garage-doors/\">\r\n                Claymont\r\n              </a>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n              Delaware City\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li class=\"service-button\">\r\n              <a href=\"https://clarkandsonsdoors.com/service-areas/hockessin-de-garage-doors/\">\r\n                Hockessin\r\n              </a>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li class=\"service-button\">\r\n              <a href=\"https://clarkandsonsdoors.com/service-areas/middletown-de-garage-doors/\">\r\n                Middletown\r\n              </a>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n              Montchanin\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li class=\"service-button\">\r\n              <a href=\"https://clarkandsonsdoors.com/service-areas/new-cas