ck levelers, seals, shelters, and bumpers to ensure safe, efficient loading and unloading at your facility. Our team keeps your loading areas running smoothly and minimizes downtime.<\\\\\\/p>\\\",\\\"url_title\\\":\\\"Loading Dock Equipment\\\",\\\"service_url\\\":\\\"https:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/clarkandsonsdoors.com\\\\\\/loading-dock\\\\\\/\\\",\\\"service_img\\\":\\\"2775\\\"}]}\",\"garage_door\":\"{\\\"checked\\\":1,\\\"door_title\\\":\\\"Common Garage\\\",\\\"door_button_name\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"door_button_url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"door_sub_title\\\":\\\"Door Problems\\\",\\\"garage_door_description\\\":\\\"<ul>\\\\r\\\\n<li>The garage door gets stuck open or closed.<\\\\\\/li>\\\\r\\\\n<li>The door moves unevenly, and from side to side.<\\\\\\/li>\\\\r\\\\n<li>You can hear loud noises when opening or closing the garage door.<\\\\\\/li>\\\\r\\\\n<li>The door falls too quickly when being lowered in manual mode.<\\\\\\/li>\\\\r\\\\n<li>The remote control door opener fails to work.<\\\\\\/li>\\\\r\\\\n<\\\\\\/ul>\\\\r\\\\n<p>If your garage door is suffering from any of these or other problems, give us a call. We will come and assess the problem and work out the best and most cost-effective solution for you.<\\\\\\/p>\\\",\\\"garage_img\\\":\\\"441\\\"}\",\"quote_sec\":\"{\\\"checked\\\":1,\\\"quote_title\\\":\\\"Contact Us Today!\\\",\\\"quotesub_title\\\":\\\"Our experts are here to help. Contact us today for fast and friendly service.\\\",\\\"quote_button_name\\\":\\\"Request Help Here\\\",\\\"quote_button_url\\\":\\\"#getafreequote\\\",\\\"quotecall_button_name\\\":\\\"CALL NOW\\\",\\\"quotecall_button_url\\\":\\\"tel:+18004793667\\\",\\\"quote_desc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"residential_sec\":\"{\\\"checked\\\":1,\\\"resi_title\\\":\\\"Garage Door Maintenance\\\",\\\"resi_sub_title\\\":\\\"Garage Door Service & Repair\\\",\\\"resi_button_name\\\":\\\"CALL NOW\\\",\\\"resi_button_url\\\":\\\"tel:+18004793667\\\",\\\"resi_description\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"gallery_sec\":\"{\\\"checked\\\":